(1, '1', '<h4>3-Reel Max Bet 2 Slots</h4>\r\n<p>The object of 8-Ball Slots is to obtain a winning symbol combination by spinning the reels.</p>\r\n<p>There are two kinds of balls in 8-Ball Slots: striped and solid. The highest symbol is the Number 8 Ball, which is neither solid nor striped.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note</strong>: There is a difference between the line bet and the total bet. The line bet shows how much you''re betting on a single payline. The total bet shows how much you''re spending in this game round. The payouts shown in the paytable are multiplied by the coin size, not the line bet. If you get winning combinations on more than one payline, the winnings for each payline are added up.</p>\r\n<h4>To play the game:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Choose the value of the coins you wish to wager each round, by clicking on the + and &ndash; buttons on the left of the screen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click Bet One or Bet Max to select the number of coins you wish to wager. Click Bet One to bet one coin, or Bet Max to bet two coins and spin the reels automatically.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>You can also bet by clicking on the corresponding column in the paytable (the left column bets one coin, the right column bets two coins). The reels will start to spin automatically.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Clicking Bet Max increases your bet to the maximum &ndash; that is, two coins &ndash; and spins the reels automatically.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Click Spin (if you did not press Bet Max or use the paytable), or click on the arm, to spin the reels. If the reels show a winning combination after they stop (along the payline), you win according to the paytable.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'en'),
(3, '1', '<h4>3-Reel Max Bet 2 Slots</h4>\r\n<p>Objek Slots 8-Ball adalah untuk mendapatkan kombinasi simbol menang dengan memutar reel.</p>\r\n<p>Ada dua jenis bola di Slots 8-Ball: bergaris dan solid. Simbol tertinggi adalah Nomor 8 Ball, yang tidak padat atau bergaris.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Harap dicatat</strong> : Ada perbedaan antara garis taruhan dan total taruhan. Taruhan garis menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda bertaruh pada payline tunggal. Total taruhan menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda menghabiskan di babak permainan ini. Pembayaran ditampilkan dalam paytable dikalikan dengan ukuran koin, bukan garis taruhan. Jika Anda mendapatkan kombinasi pemenang pada lebih dari satu payline, kemenangan untuk setiap payline yang ditambahkan.</p>\r\n<h4>Untuk memainkan permainan:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Pilih nilai dari uang yang Anda ingin bertaruh setiap putaran, dengan mengklik + dan - tombol di sebelah kiri layar.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Klik Bet Satu atau Bet Max untuk memilih jumlah uang yang Anda ingin bertaruh. Klik Bet Satu bertaruh satu koin, atau Bet Max untuk bertaruh dua koin dan memutar gulungan secara otomatis.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Anda juga bisa bertaruh dengan mengklik pada kolom yang sesuai dalam paytable (kolom taruhan kiri satu koin, kolom taruhan kanan dua koin). Gulungan akan mulai berputar secara otomatis.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Mengklik Bet Max meningkatkan taruhan Anda secara maksimal - yaitu, dua koin - dan berputar gulungan otomatis.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Klik Putar (jika Anda tidak menekan Bet Max atau menggunakan paytable), atau klik pada lengan, untuk memutar gulungan. Jika gulungan menunjukkan kombinasi yang unggul setelah mereka berhenti (sepanjang payline), Anda menang berdasarkan paytable.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'id'),
(4, '1', '<h4>3-Reel Max Bet 2 Slots</h4>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Slots 8-Ball l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p>C&oacute; hai lo&#7841;i b&oacute;ng trong Slots 8-Ball: s&#7885;c v&agrave; v&#7919;ng ch&#7855;c. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng cao nh&#7845;t l&agrave; s&#7889; 8 Ball, &#273;&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; r&#7855;n c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng s&#7885;c.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;</strong> : C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t.T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang chi ti&ecirc;u trong v&ograve;ng &#273;&#7845;u n&agrave;y. To&aacute;n t&#7927; l&#7879; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu, kh&ocirc;ng c&#432;&#7907;c line. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<h4>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Ch&#7885;n gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i v&ograve;ng, b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t + v&agrave; - tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o Bet M&#7897;t ho&#7863;c Bet Max &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c. Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o Bet One &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu, ho&#7863;c Bet Max &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c hai &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n v&agrave; xoay gu&#7891;ng t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o c&aacute;c c&#7897;t t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng trong paytable (c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7897;t b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu, c&#7897;t c&#432;&#7907;c ngay hai &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n). C&aacute;c cu&#7897;n s&#7869; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u quay t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;p Bet Max t&#259;ng &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; t&#7889;i &#273;a - &#273;&oacute; l&agrave;, hai &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n - v&agrave; quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o Spin (n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7845;n Bet Max ho&#7863;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng paytable), ho&#7863;c click v&agrave;o c&aacute;nh tay, &#273;&#7875; xoay gu&#7891;ng. N&#7871;u c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau khi h&#7885; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i (c&ugrave;ng payline), b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng theo paytable.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'vn'),
