(9, '4', '<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Alien Hunter l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<h4>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Ch&#7885;n k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t + v&agrave; - tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o Bet m&#7895;i n&uacute;t Line. M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c line. C&aacute;c con s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c n&uacute;t tr&ecirc;n c&#7843; hai b&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n cho bi&#7871;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n hi&#7879;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline. M&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#7871;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n t&#7889;i &#273;a, nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a s&#7869; thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p l&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Ch&#7885;n payline c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t Select Lines th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t payline, ho&#7863;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c n&uacute;t m&agrave;u tr&ecirc;n c&#7843; hai m&#7863;t c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng.B&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t payline cao h&#417;n, b&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7885;n t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p h&#417;n (v&iacute; d&#7909;, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline 18, payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 17 s&#7869; l&agrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; l&agrave; t&#7889;t). B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p Bet Max &#273;&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c payline v&agrave; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>S&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i l&agrave; d&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o Spin (n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7845;n Bet Max) &#273;&#7875; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau khi h&#7885; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i (c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t payline b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o), b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng theo b&#7843;ng th&#7855;ng. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t paytable &#273;&#7875; xem paytable, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n. &#272;&oacute;ng paytable b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t Back. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u payline &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>payline:</h4>\r\n<p>payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline v&agrave; xem h&igrave;nh d&#7841;ng c&#7911;a h&#7885; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p n&uacute;t Select Lines.</p>\r\n<p>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;: B&#7841;n ch&#7881; c&oacute; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng n&#7871;u k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7841;o th&agrave;nh c&aacute;c k&yacute; hi&#7879;u li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; gu&#7891;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; cho quy t&#7855;c &#273;&oacute;. T&igrave;m hi&#7875;u th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;: C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t.T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang chi ti&ecirc;u trong v&ograve;ng &#273;&#7845;u n&agrave;y. To&aacute;n t&#7927; l&#7879; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line, kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7857;ng t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<h4>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</h4>\r\n<p>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n paytable. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, nh&acirc;n d&ograve;ng c&aacute; l&agrave; do thanh to&aacute;n.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u hai k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p>S&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; gu&#7891;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, v&agrave; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7843;i n&#7857;m trong m&#7897;t h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c (tr&#7915; Scatter v&agrave; Bonus), &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o th&agrave;nh s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n thanh to&aacute;n ri&ecirc;ng cho c&aacute;c k&yacute; hi&#7879;u hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n<h4>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter</h4>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline c&#7909; th&#7875; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi nh&#432; l&agrave; m&#7897;t s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng; n&#7871;u c&oacute; ba ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n trong s&#7889; h&#7885; b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tr&ograve; ch&#417;i, b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; (kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&#7845;u tr&#7915; t&#7915; s&#7889; d&#432; cho h&#7885;). S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin ph&#7841;t cho m&#7895;i s&#7889; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; tr&ecirc;n paytable. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nhi&#7873;u spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; trong m&#7897;t spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</p>\r\n<h4>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng bonus</h4>\r\n<p>C&oacute; hai v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng kh&aacute;c nhau trong Alien Hunter.</p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&#7913;ng, n&#7857;m r&#7843;i r&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n nh&#7919;ng &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7847;u v&agrave; cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng, &#273;&#432;a b&#7841;n v&agrave;o v&ograve;ng thu th&#7853;p ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng. &#7902; &#273;&acirc;y b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o tr&#7913;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&agrave;i h&agrave;nh tinh: h&#7847;u h&#7871;t trong s&#7889; h&#7885; c&oacute; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng (nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng s&#7889; c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n) v&agrave; m&#7897;t ch&#7913;a m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n m&agrave; t&#259;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a tr&#7913;ng b&#7841;n click v&agrave;o sau khi t&igrave;m th&#7845;y n&oacute;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng qu&#7843; tr&#7913;ng ch&#7913;a c&aacute;c ""headjumper"" ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&agrave;i h&agrave;nh tinh &aacute;c. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n b&#7845;m v&agrave;o tr&#7913;ng c&#7911;a headjumper, v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng l&agrave; h&#417;n. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n b&#7845;m v&agrave;o tr&#7913;ng c&#7911;a headjumper v&agrave;o th&#7917; &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch.</p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng phi h&agrave;nh th&#432;&#7903;ng, xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n ba l&#7847;n tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng (tr&ecirc;n ba cu&#7897;n gi&#7919;a) s&#7869; &#273;&#432;a b&#7841;n v&agrave;o v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng s&#259;n b&#7855;n.&#7902; &#273;&acirc;y b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i b&#7845;m v&agrave;o ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&agrave;i h&agrave;nh tinh xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n. B&#7841;n c&oacute; hai l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>K&#7929; n&#259;ng - b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i n&#7855;m b&#7855;t 6 ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&agrave;i h&agrave;nh tinh trong v&ograve;ng 15 gi&acirc;y. chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&agrave;i h&agrave;nh tinh b&#7841;n b&#7855;t - m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&agrave; nhanh h&#417;n so v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c, v&agrave; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; h&#417;n. Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng qu&#7843;n l&yacute; &#273;&#7875; n&#7855;m b&#7855;t b&#7845;t k&#7923; ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&agrave;i h&agrave;nh tinh.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Luck - ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&agrave;i h&agrave;nh tinh di chuy&#7875;n ch&#7853;m h&#417;n v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; th&#7901;i h&#7841;n, nh&#432;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Dollar b&oacute;ng</h4>\r\n<p>&#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t lotto lo&#7841;i sidegame ti&#7871;n b&#7897; n&#417;i b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n 5 con s&#7889; ra kh&#7887;i 49. Sau &#273;&oacute;, m&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, n&#259;m con s&#7889; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c r&uacute;t ra m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n. C&aacute;c con s&#7889; h&#417;n ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, b&#7841;n c&agrave;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. N&#7871;u t&#7845;t c&#7843; n&#259;m con s&#7889; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p, b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>Dollar b&oacute;ng n&#7857;m &#7903; ph&#7847;n tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. B&#7845;m v&agrave;o Enable &#273;&#7875; ch&#417;i n&oacute;. B&#7841;n s&#7869; th&#7845;y m&#7897;t t&#7853;p h&#7907;p c&aacute;c s&#7889; t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 49. Click v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#259;m ng&#432;&#7901;i h&#7885; ch&#7885;n th&#7911; c&ocirc;ng (click l&#7847;n n&#7919;a &#273;&#7875; b&#7887; ch&#7885;n), ho&#7863;c nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; n&oacute; l&agrave;m cho b&#7841;n t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n thay &#273;&#7893;i s&#7889; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n, nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o b&#7845;t k&#7923; c&#7911;a c&aacute;c con s&#7889; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n ch&uacute;ng, v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i m&#7899;i. Nh&#7845;n Activate &#273;&#7875; &#7849;n c&aacute;c con s&#7889; v&agrave; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Trong khi b&oacute;ng Dollar &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, m&#7897;t &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot b&#7893; sung &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng m&#7895;i khi b&#7841;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n m&#7897;t &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh. Gi&aacute; tr&#7883; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot l&agrave; c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; t&igrave;m th&#7845;y n&oacute; trong giao di&#7879;n Dollar Ball. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n h&#7911;y b&#7887; Ball tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Dollar, nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o Disable.</p>\r\n<p>Dollar Ball s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i m&#7885;i tr&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;u ch&iacute;nh tr&ograve;n, v&#7899;i c&aacute;c con s&#7889; t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921;, cho &#273;&#7871;n khi b&#7841;n c&oacute; thay &#273;&#7893;i s&#7889; ho&#7863;c v&ocirc; hi&#7879;u h&oacute;a c&aacute;c sidegame.</p>\r\n<p>con s&#7889; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong m&#7897;t h&agrave;ng v&ograve;ng tr&ograve;n m&agrave;u tr&#7855;ng &#7903; ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. M&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&#7919;ng con s&#7889; r&uacute;t s&#7869; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n ngay p