(14, '3', '<h4>Slots 3 Reel v&#7899;i m&#7897;t ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i</h4>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Lab c&#7911;a Alchemist l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<h4>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o Bet One, Bet Hai ho&#7863;c Bet Max (= ba) &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c. gi&aacute; tr&#7883; &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; &#7903; g&oacute;c tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. C&aacute;c cu&#7897;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u quay.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau khi h&#7885; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i (c&ugrave;ng payline), b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng theo b&#7843;ng th&#7855;ng (xem b&#7843;ng &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n c&#7911;a m&aacute;y).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Bonus Game:</h4>\r\n<p>Bonus Slot m&aacute;y ch&#7913;a m&#7897;t tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng. &#272;&#7875; truy c&#7853;p v&agrave;o c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng, b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ba bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng cu&#7889;n s&aacute;ch. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng, b&#7845;m ba chai tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. Sau &#273;&oacute; b&#7841;n s&#7869; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n t&ugrave;y thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a chai c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p>\r\n<h4>N&uacute;t:</h4>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Bet M&#7897;t</td>\r\n<td>&#272;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu v&agrave; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Bet Hai</td>\r\n<td>Bet hai &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n v&agrave; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Bet Max</td>\r\n<td>&#272;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c t&#7845;t c&#7843; ba ti&#7873;n xu v&agrave; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;: C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t.T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang chi ti&ecirc;u trong v&ograve;ng &#273;&#7845;u n&agrave;y. To&aacute;n t&#7927; l&#7879; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu, kh&ocirc;ng c&#432;&#7907;c line. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<h4>Quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; c&#7847;u th&#7911;</h4>\r\n<p>T&#7927; l&#7879; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i (RTP) l&agrave; 97,32%.</p>', 'vn'),
