(19, 'B', '<p><strong>5-Reel Slots 20-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a khe Got Talent c&#7911;a Anh l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p + v&agrave; &acirc; &euro; "b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>d&ograve;ng Bet</strong> &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng ho&#7863;c gi&#7843;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng.</li>\r\n<li>Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh d&#7841;ng c&#7911;a h&#7885; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p + v&agrave; &acirc; &euro; "b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> . Payline c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c n&uacute;t s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n ph&iacute;a c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng. L&#7921;a ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t payline cao bao g&#7891;m t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p qu&aacute;. V&iacute; d&#7909;, ch&#7885;n payline 6 c&#361;ng k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 5. Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i tr&#7853;n v&ograve;ng b&#7857;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n. T&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong <strong>T&#7893;ng Bet</strong> h&#7897;p ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n <strong>Autoplay</strong> n&uacute;t.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Ch&#417;i</strong> quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873; v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c line hi&#7879;n h&agrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>Cu&#7897;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xoay s&#7869; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng Autoplay. Click v&agrave;o <strong>Autoplay</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y ch&#7885;n. Ch&#7885;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&oacute;. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>ch&#417;i</strong> b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u c&aacute;c ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng Autoplay. Trong Autoplay, s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin c&ograve;n l&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh, khi b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; kinh ph&iacute; &#273;&#7875; quay ti&#7871;p theo, ho&#7863;c khi m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t.B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c quay t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7899;m b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> , n&#7857;m &#8203;&#8203;b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>T&#7893;ng Bet</strong> h&#7897;p.</li>\r\n<li>Th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo paytable. Gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; b&#7857;ng &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i gi&aacute; tr&#7883; t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. C&aacute;c paytable c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ch&#7881; c&oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n. th&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n payline kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i s&#7869; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y, c&#361;ng nh&#432; c&oacute; d&ograve;ng ghi danh th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>trang th&ocirc;ng tin:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Info</strong> m&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau.Nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o c&aacute;c n&uacute;t v&#7899;i t&ecirc;n trang &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; cho ph&eacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&aacute;c nhau.Ngo&agrave;i ra, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o m&#361;i t&ecirc;n n&#7857;m b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i v&agrave; b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a c&aacute;c n&uacute;t n&agrave;y.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Ti&#7873;n chung</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Live Show Bonus pt. 1</strong> v&agrave; <strong>Live Show Bonus pt. 2</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;ch v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; ph&aacute;c th&#7843;o c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c c&#7911;a n&oacute;.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Bonus quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch quy lu&#7853;t c&#7911;a n&oacute;.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Win d&ograve;ng</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh minh h&#7885;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline c&oacute; th&#7875; v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c cho vi&#7879;c t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a h&#7885;.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Reels</strong> tho&aacute;t ra kh&#7887;i m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh chi&#7871;u v&agrave; tr&#7843; l&#7841;i cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n <strong>Ti&#7873;n chung</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c trang Th&ocirc;ng tin. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; gu&#7891;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, v&agrave; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7843;i li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Win H&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#7889;i &#273;a</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a trong game c&oacute; m&#7897;t gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n tr&ecirc;n. &#272;&#7875; bi&#7871;t th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng tin, xem c&aacute;c &#272;i&#7873;u kho&#7843;n v&agrave; &#272;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n ph&#7847;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>T&#7921; ch&#7841;y</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Gi&#7919; n&uacute;t SPIN 2 gi&acirc;y v&agrave;o c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; m&#7903; ra m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n Autoplay.</li>\r\n<li>B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t v&agrave;i c&#432;&#7907;c t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng, m&#7897;t sau khi kh&aacute;c.</li>\r\n<li>&#272;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u m&#7897;t phi&ecirc;n Auto Play, tr&#432;&#7899;c ti&ecirc;n b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p m&#7897;t s&#7889; th&ocirc;ng s&#7889;:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>S&#7889; Auto Play quay.</li>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n T&#7893;ng thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i t&#7889;i &#273;a. Khi con s&#7889; n&agrave;y &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave; b&#7883; m&#7845;t trong m&#7897;t phi&ecirc;n Auto Play, k&#7923; h&#7885;p s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c.</li>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n duy nh&#7845;t. Khi m&#7897;t Auto Play gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng quay m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng m&agrave; l&agrave; b&#7857;ng ho&#7863;c cao h&#417;n gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n n&agrave;y, phi&ecirc;n Auto Play s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Khi c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p, nh&#7845;n "CONFIRM" &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u phi&ecirc;n Auto Play. B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7845;m v&agrave;o n&uacute;t "EXIT" &#273;&#7875; &#273;&oacute;ng m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n Auto Play.</li>\r\n<li>B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; ng&#7915;ng quay t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c &#273;&#7871;n spin ti&#7871;p theo b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch khai th&aacute;c c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</li>\r\n<li>spin t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7869; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i n&#7871;u c&oacute; c&aacute;c &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n sau &#273;&acirc;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t.</li>\r\n<li>Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; kinh ph&iacute; &#273;&#7875; quay ti&#7871;p theo.</li>\r\n<li>Gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n T&#7893;ng thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i t&#7889;i &#273;a &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng duy nh&#7845;t l&agrave; &#273;&#7841;t.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>hoang d&atilde; Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild <img src="../img/ashbgt_wild.jpg" alt="" />c&oacute; th&#7875; thay th&#7871; cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; vi&#7879;c khen th&#432;&#7903;ng v&agrave; mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n thanh to&aacute;n ri&ecirc;ng cho 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&#432; &#273;&atilde; th&#7845;y trong paytable. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843; thay v&igrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n n&#7871;u s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; Wilds l&agrave; l&#7899;n h&#417;n so v&#7899;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n (b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7913;ng Wild).</p>\r\n<p><strong>bonus Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#432;&#7903;ng trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i l&agrave; <img src="../img/ashbgt_bonus.jpg" alt="" />. N&#7871;u n&oacute; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i &#7903; b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 1, 3 v&agrave; 5 sau m&#7897;t spin tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, c&aacute;c <strong>Live Show Bonus</strong> &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; <strong>Live Show th&#432;&#7903;ng</strong> c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y <a href="#">&#7903; &#273;&acirc;y</a> .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Khi bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; <img src="../img/ashbgt_fs.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i &#7903; b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 2, 4 v&agrave; 5 sau m&#7897;t spin tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, <strong>mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay</strong> t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c <strong>spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y <a href="#">&#7903; &#273;&acirc;y</a> .</p>\r\n<p><strong><a name="ashbgt_live_bonus"></a>Live Show Bonus</strong></p>\r\n<p>Live Show Bonus &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7903;i s&#7921; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i c&#7911;a c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Bonus <img src="../img/ashbgt_bonus.jpg" alt="" />b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 1, 3 v&agrave; 5 sau m&#7897;t spin tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p>Tr&#432;&#7899;c khi b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u ph&#7847;n th&#432;&#7903;ng, b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7855;c ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t lo&#7841;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng, m&agrave; b&#7841;n s&#7869; qua v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7843;. C&oacute; 3 l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n: Nh&#7841;c &#272;&#7841;o Lu&#7853;t, Lu&#7853;t Dance v&agrave; &#272;&#7841;o lu&#7853;t m&#7899;i l&#7841;. M&#7895;i th&#7875; lo&#7841;i c&oacute; 8 th&iacute; sinh.</p>\r\n<p>M&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t lo&#7841;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&#7845;p <strong>Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c</strong> s&#7869; &#273;&#432;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t b&aacute;nh xe v&#7899;i c&aacute;c k&yacute; t&#7921; t&#7915; lo&#7841;i &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>spin</strong> n&uacute;t quay b&aacute;nh xe. N&oacute; s&#7869; &#273;&#7893; b&#7897; l&ecirc;n m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh nh&acirc;n v&#7853;t v&agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y s&#7869; l&agrave; th&iacute; sinh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n trong su&#7889;t Live Show Bonus.</p>\r\n<p>Ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng c&oacute; 3 giai &#273;o&#7841;n: Audition, Semi-Finals v&agrave; chung k&#7871;t. M&#7895;i ph&ograve;ng trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n di&#7877;n ra nh&#432; m&ocirc; t&#7843; d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.</p>\r\n<p>M&#7897;t &#273;o&#7841;n video c&#7911;a h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong c&aacute;c giai &#273;o&#7841;n. C&aacute;c to h&#417;n c&aacute;c kh&aacute;n gi&#7843; hoan ngh&ecirc;nh h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, cao h&#417;n c&aacute;c V&#7895; tay-o-Meter b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n s&#7869; t&#259;ng l&ecirc;n. C&aacute;c m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; c&#7911;a n&oacute; cao h&#417;n, cao h&#417;n c&aacute;c nh&acirc;n b&#7841;n s&#7869; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n t&#7915; m&#7897;t giai &#273;o&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; nh&acirc;n &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;ang ph&aacute;t, th&#7849;m ph&aacute;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;n c&ograve;i c&#7911;a h&#7885; v&agrave; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng l&ecirc;n m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng Xs tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh, m&agrave; s&#7869; gi&#7843;m V&#7895; tay-o-Meter. N&#7871;u t&#7845;t c&#7843; 4 Xs &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7855;p s&aacute;ng, v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c. N&#7871;u giai &#273;o&#7841;n hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i k&#7871;t th&uacute;c tr&#432;&#7899;c khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; 4 Xs &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7855;p s&aacute;ng, sau &#273;&oacute; b&#7841;n s&#7869; ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh giai &#273;o&#7841;n ti&#7871;p theo. S&#7921; ti&#7871;n b&#7897; c&#7911;a m&#7897;t giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7881; &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7903;i m&#7897;t thanh ti&#7871;n tr&igrave;nh &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a video.</p>\r\n<p>Sau m&#7895;i giai &#273;o&#7841;n, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh t&#7893;ng k&#7871;t ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7915; giai &#273;o&#7841;n hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883;.</p>\r\n<p>Giai &#273;o&#7841;n Audition c&oacute; th&#7875; c&#7845;p cho m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n 7-25.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c giai &#273;o&#7841;n V&ograve;ng b&aacute;n k&#7871;t c&oacute; th&#7875; c&#7845;p cho m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n 12-100.</p>\r\n<p>Giai &#273;o&#7841;n Finals c&oacute; th&#7875; c&#7845;p cho m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n 50-1000.</p>\r\n<p>Sau v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng to&agrave;n b&#7897; &#273;&atilde; xong, ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7915; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o v&#7899;i nhau &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o th&agrave;nh t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng.</p>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;n <strong>OK</strong> &#273;&#7875; quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>L&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> Trong khi ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;ang di&#7877;n ra, c&aacute;c <strong>Skip</strong> n&uacute;t c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &eacute;p &#273;&#7875; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng k&#7871;t th&uacute;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng. B&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a &#273;&#7871;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh th&#7855;ng t&oacute;m t&#7855;t v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a name="ashbgt_freespins"></a>quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7903;i s&#7921; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i c&#7911;a Spin bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; <img src="../img/ashbgt_fs.jpg" alt="" />b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 2, 4 v&agrave; 5 sau m&#7897;t spin tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p>M&#7895;i bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; s&#7869; ti&#7871;t l&#7897; m&#7897;t s&#7889; ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n. Nh&#7919;ng con s&#7889; n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o v&#7899;i nhau &#273;&#7875; cung c&#7845;p cho t&#7893;ng s&#7889; spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng cao nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng l&agrave; 20. M&#7913;c th&#7845;p nh&#7845;t l&agrave; 7.</p>\r\n<p>Tr&#432;&#7899;c khi quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, Ch&#7845;n g&ocirc; ng&ocirc;i sao t&agrave;i n&#259;ng c&#7911;a n&#432;&#7899;c Anh s&#7869; bay qua c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&agrave; &#273;&#7845;t tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n (gi&#7919;a 3 v&agrave; 5) c&#7911;a c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chuy&#7875;n th&agrave;nh Wilds v&agrave; s&#7869; v&#7851;n &acirc; &euro; &oelig;stuck&acirc; &euro; ?? t&#7841;i ch&#7895; cho to&agrave;n b&#7897; th&#7901;i gian c&#7911;a t&#7921; do quay v&ograve;ng.</p>\r\n<p>Trong spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n xoay s&#7869; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; tr&ecirc;n m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng v&agrave; s&#7889; d&ograve;ng nh&#432; v&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c th&#7855;ng t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n<p>Vi&#7879;c <strong>mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin T&#7893;ng Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c hi&#7879;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7915; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; ch&#417;i cho &#273;&#7871;n nay. S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin tr&#7889;ng c&ograve;n l&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng.</p>\r\n<p>Sau khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7897;ng d&#7891;n t&#7915; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. Nh&#7845;n <strong>OK</strong>&#273;&#7875; quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; c&#7847;u th&#7911;</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&#7927; l&#7879; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i (RTP) l&agrave; 92,52%.</p>', 'vn'),
