(22, '29', '<p><strong>5-reel 20-line slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>The objective of the Full Moon Fortunes slot is to obtain winning symbol combinations by spinning the reels.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To play the game:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Line bets are chosen by clicking + and &ndash; below <strong>Line Bet</strong> to increase or decrease the amount.</li>\r\n<li>The Full Moon Fortunes game is always played with 20 active paylines. The number of active paylines is fixed and cannot be changed by the player.</li>\r\n<li>Your total bet per game round equals your selected line bet multiplied by the number of active paylines. The total amount you have bet will be shown in the <strong>Total Bet</strong> box above the <strong>Auto Play</strong> button.</li>\r\n<li>Hover over a symbol on the reels to display the potential payouts for this symbol.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Spin</strong> spins the reels with the current selection of lines and line bets.</li>\r\n<li>Reels can be spun automatically using the Auto Play function. <br />Click on the <strong>Auto Play</strong> button to display the list of options. Select the number of spins to be played automatically by clicking on it. This also starts the function. During Auto Play, the <strong>Auto Play</strong> button displays the number of spins remaining. The mode ends when the reels have been spun the number of times you have determined, when you do not have sufficient funds for the next spin, or when the Free Spins feature is triggered. You can end automatic spins early by clicking <strong>Stop Auto Play</strong>, located in the lower right-hand corner of the game window.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Turbo</strong> within the Auto Play options turns the Turbo Mode on or off. Turning it on speeds up the reel spins during Auto Play.</li>\r\n<li>Wins are calculated according to the paytable. Your line win will equal your line bet multiplied by the corresponding value according to the paytable. The paytable can be accessed via the <strong>Info</strong> page, on the <strong>Payouts</strong> screen.</li>\r\n<li>On a given payline, only the highest payline winning combination pays. Simultaneous winnings on different paylines are accumulated.</li>\r\n<li>In case of a winning spin, the <strong>Win</strong> field at the bottom of the game window displays the accumulated winnings.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Info pages:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Info</strong> opens the reference screens describing different game components. Clicking the <strong>&lt;&lt;</strong> and <strong>&gt;&gt;</strong> buttons in the lower right-hand corner of the screen enables navigating between the different screens. Another way of switching between the screens is by clicking on the buttons with page names in the upper part of the window.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The <strong>Payouts</strong> screen shows all winning combinations (the &ldquo;paytable&rdquo;).</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Full Moon</strong> screen explains the Full Moon feature.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Free Spins</strong> screen describes the symbol combination necessary to trigger the feature and explains its rules.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paylines</strong> screen illustrates all possible paylines and explains the rules for calculating their wins.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Back to Reels</strong> exits the reference screen and returns to the game.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Paylines are represented by lines that appear over the reels. All 20 paylines are illustrated on the <strong>Paylines</strong> page.</li>\r\n<li>All 20 paylines are always active and can register wins.</li>\r\n<li>There is a difference between the line bet and the total bet. The line bet shows how much is being bet on a single payline. The total bet shows how much is being bet in total on the game round. Payouts shown in the paytable (on the <strong>Payouts</strong> page) are multiplied by the line bet.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>About payouts:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payouts are listed in the paytable on the <strong>Payouts</strong> screen. To find the possible win amount, the line bet must be multiplied by the payout.</li>\r\n<li>If two payline winning combinations occur on the same line, the higher of them is paid out. If more than one active payline has a winning combination, the winnings are accumulated.</li>\r\n<li>Winning combinations must start from the left most reel, and the symbols have to be consecutive.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Win Limit</strong></p>\r\n<p>The maximum win in the game has an upper limit. For more information, see the Terms and Conditions section.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Wild Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Wild symbol <img src="../img/ashfmf_wild.jpg" alt="" /> can stand for any other symbol, except for the Full Moon Scatter and Free Spin Bonus scatter symbols, to make the best possible winning combination. There is also a separate payout for 3 or more Wild symbols on an active payline, as seen in the paytable. This is paid out instead of the regular symbol win if the win amount from Wilds is larger than the win from the regular symbols (in winning lines where the Wild is standing in for other symbols).</p>\r\n<p><strong>Full Moon Scatter Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Full Moon Scatter symbol <img src="../img/ashfmf_fullmoon.jpg" alt="" /> appears on reel 5 during the main game only. When it appears, all Dr Blackwood symbols <img src="../img/ashfmf_drblackwood.jpg" alt="" />currently on the reels are turned into Multiplier Wild symbols <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />. More information on the Multiplier Wild symbol can be found below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Multiplier Wild Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Multiplier Wild symbol <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" /> can substitute for any other symbol except for the Full Moon Scatter and Free Spin Bonus scatter symbols, to make the best possible winning combination. In addition, line wins resulting from a combination in which the Multiplier Wild symbol participates are multiplied by the value shown on the symbol. The multiplier value awarded is random and can be from x1 to x5.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> All <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" /> symbols count up to the same multiplier value. If there are 2 or more such symbols, their multiplier values are not added up. For example, if on a winning payline there are 3 <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" /> symbols with a multiplier value x2, the line win will only be multiplied by x2.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> When not substituting for any other symbols, <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" /> symbols pay out as multiplied Dr Blackwood symbols.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Free Spin Bonus Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>3, 4 or 5 Free Spin Bonus scatter symbols <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" /> appearing simultaneously anywhere on the reels during the main game trigger the Free Spins feature.</p>\r\n<p>More information on the Free Spins feature can be found <a href="#">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stacked Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Dragon Jewel symbol <img src="../img/ashfmf_stacked.jpg" alt="" /> is stacked on all reels. This means that Dragon Jewel symbols appear one above the other on the reels, thus making higher payouts possible.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Full Moon Feature</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Full Moon feature is triggered when the Full Moon Scatter symbol <img src="../img/ashfmf_fullmoon.jpg" alt="" /> appears on reel 5 during the main game as explained above in the <strong>Full Moon Scatter Symbol</strong> section.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a name="ashfmf_frees"></a>Free Spins</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Free Spins feature will have a different number of free spins and a different win multiplier depending on the number of <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" />symbols that have triggered it.</p>\r\n<table class="table"><colgroup><col width="250" /><col width="250" /><col width="250" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr><th><strong>Number of <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" /> symbols <br />triggering Free Spins</strong></th><th><strong>Initial number of free spins <br />awarded</strong></th><th><strong>Initial win multiplier value <br />awarded</strong></th></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n<td><center>1</center></td>\r\n<td><center>1</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>4</center></td>\r\n<td><center>2</center></td>\r\n<td><center>2</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>5</center></td>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>When Free Spins is triggered, you will be taken to a graveyard, where you need to pick graves. Click on a grave to pick it. Each grave will award either an additional number of free spins (from 1 to 4), or an additional win multiplier value (from x1 to x4), which will be added to the initial values that you have won. When a grave you have picked reveals <strong>Collect</strong>, the picking is terminated. Clicking<strong>Continue</strong> on the screen that appears afterwards starts Free Spins.</p>\r\n<p>The <strong>Free Spins</strong> box to the upper left of the game window shows the accumulated free spins you have won. The <strong>Multiplier</strong> box to the upper right of the game window displays the accumulated win multiplier value. The win multiplier value does not change after the picking stage has finished. All line wins during Free Spins are multiplied by that value.</p>\r\n<p>The highest number of free spins you can win altogether is 20. The highest multiplier value is 5.</p>\r\n<p>During Free Spins all <img src="../img/ashfmf_drblackwood.jpg" alt="" /> symbols act as Multiplier Wilds, multiplying line wins by up to 25.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Multiplier Wild multipliers are pre-calculated to account for the free spins multiplier.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>During Free Spins, the reels are spun automatically using the same bet per line as on the spin that won the feature.</p>\r\n<p>After each spin, the win for that spin is displayed in the <strong>Win</strong> field. The <strong>Free Spins Total</strong> field shows the accumulated winnings from all free spins played so far. The number of free spins remaining is shown in the <strong>Free Spins</strong> box.</p>\r\n<p>After all Free Spins have been completed a screen appears showing the accumulated winnings from all free spins. Click <strong>Continue</strong> to return to the main game reels.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>The theoretical percentage return to player (RTP) is 94.01%.</p>', 'en'),
(23, '29', '<p><strong>5-reel slot 20-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tujuan dari slot Fortunes Full Moon adalah untuk mendapatkan kombinasi simbol menang dengan memutar reel.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Untuk memainkan permainan:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Taruhan baris yang dipilih dengan mengklik + dan - di bawah <strong>garis Bet</strong> untuk menambah atau mengurangi jumlah.</li>\r\n<li>The Full Moon Fortunes permainan selalu dimainkan dengan 20 paylines aktif. Jumlah paylines aktif adalah tetap dan tidak dapat diubah oleh pemain.</li>\r\n<li>Total taruhan Anda per game putaran sama taruhan baris yang dipilih Anda dikalikan dengan jumlah paylines aktif. Jumlah total yang Anda telah bertaruh akan ditampilkan dalam <strong>Jumlah Bet</strong> kotak di atas <strong>Auto Play</strong> tombol.</li>\r\n<li>Arahkan kursor simbol pada gulungan untuk menampilkan pembayaran potensi simbol ini.</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>spin</strong> berputar gulungan dengan pilihan saat ini dari garis dan garis taruhan.</li>\r\n<li>Gulungan dapat berputar secara otomatis menggunakan fungsi Auto Play. <br />Klik pada <strong>Auto Play</strong> tombol untuk menampilkan daftar pilihan. Pilih jumlah berputar untuk dimainkan secara otomatis dengan mengkliknya. Ini juga mulai fungsi. Selama Auto Play, <strong>Auto Putar</strong> tombol menampilkan jumlah spin tersisa. Modus berakhir bila gulungan telah berputar jumlah kali Anda telah menentukan, ketika Anda tidak memiliki dana yang cukup untuk spin berikutnya, atau ketika fitur Free Spins dipicu. Anda dapat mengakhiri berputar otomatis awal dengan mengklik <strong>Berhenti Auto Play</strong> , yang terletak di sudut kanan bawah dari jendela permainan.</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Turbo</strong> dalam opsi Auto Play ternyata Turbo Mode atau menonaktifkan. Menyalakannya kecepatan hingga reel berputar selama Auto Play.</li>\r\n<li>Menang dihitung berdasarkan paytable tersebut. Garis menang Anda akan sama taruhan baris Anda dikalikan dengan nilai yang sesuai menurut paytable. Paytable dapat diakses melalui <strong>Info</strong> halaman, pada <strong>Pembayaran</strong> layar.</li>\r\n<li>Pada payline diberikan, hanya tertinggi kombinasi payline menang membayar. kemenangan simultan pada paylines yang berbeda diakumulasi.</li>\r\n<li>Dalam kasus spin menang, <strong>Win</strong> lapangan di bagian bawah dari jendela permainan menampilkan kemenangan akumulasi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>halaman info:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Info</strong> membuka layar referensi yang menggambarkan komponen permainan yang berbeda. Mengklik <strong>&lt;&lt;</strong> dan <strong>&gt;&gt;</strong> tombol di sudut kanan bawah layar memungkinkan navigasi antara layar yang berbeda. Cara lain untuk beralih antara layar adalah dengan mengklik tombol dengan nama halaman di bagian atas jendela.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The <strong>Pembayaran</strong> layar menunjukkan semua kombinasi pemenang (yang "paytable").</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Full Moon</strong> layar menjelaskan fitur Full Moon.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Gratis Spins</strong> layar menggambarkan kombinasi simbol yang diperlukan untuk memicu fitur dan menjelaskan aturan.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paylines</strong> layar menggambarkan semua paylines mungkin dan menjelaskan aturan untuk menghitung kemenangan mereka.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Kembali ke gulungan</strong> keluar layar referensi dan kembali ke permainan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Paylines diwakili oleh garis-garis yang muncul di atas gulungan. Semua 20 paylines diilustrasikan pada <strong>Paylines</strong> halaman.</li>\r\n<li>Semua 20 paylines selalu aktif dan dapat mendaftar menang.</li>\r\n<li>Ada perbedaan antara garis taruhan dan total taruhan. Taruhan garis menunjukkan berapa banyak yang bertaruh pada payline tunggal. Total taruhan menunjukkan berapa banyak yang bertaruh secara total pada putaran permainan. Pembayaran ditampilkan dalam paytable (pada<strong>pembayaran</strong> halaman) dikalikan dengan taruhan baris.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Tentang pembayaran:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pembayaran tercantum dalam paytable pada <strong>pembayaran</strong> layar. Untuk menemukan jumlah menang mungkin, garis taruhan harus dikalikan dengan payout.</li>\r\n<li>Jika dua kombinasi pemenang payline terjadi pada baris yang sama, lebih tinggi dari mereka dibayarkan. Jika lebih dari satu payline aktif memiliki kombinasi menang, kemenangan diakumulasikan.</li>\r\n<li>Kombinasi pemenang harus mulai dari gulungan paling kiri, dan simbol harus berturut-turut.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Win Batas Maksimum</strong></p>\r\n<p>Kemenangan maksimum dalam permainan memiliki batas atas. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, lihat Syarat dan Ketentuan bagian.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Simbol wild</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simbol liar <img src="../img/ashfmf_wild.jpg" alt="" />bisa berdiri untuk setiap simbol lain, kecuali untuk Full Moon Menyebarkan dan spin Bonus simbol pencar Gratis, untuk membuat kombinasi pemenang terbaik. Ada juga pembayaran terpisah untuk 3 atau lebih simbol Wild pada payline aktif, seperti yang terlihat dalam paytable.Ini dibayarkan bukan kemenangan simbol biasa jika jumlah menang dari Wilds lebih besar daripada menang dari simbol biasa (dalam memenangkan baris mana liar yang berdiri di atas simbol-simbol lainnya).</p>\r\n<p><strong>Full Moon sebar Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simbol Full Moon Menyebarkan <img src="../img/ashfmf_fullmoon.jpg" alt="" />muncul pada reel 5 selama pertandingan utama saja. Ketika muncul, semua simbol Dr Blackwood <img src="../img/ashfmf_drblackwood.jpg" alt="" />saat ini di gulungan berubah menjadi Multiplier simbol liar <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />. Informasi lebih lanjut tentang simbol Multiplier liar dapat ditemukan di bawah.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Multiplier Simbol Wild</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simbol Multiplier liar <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />dapat menggantikan simbol lain kecuali untuk Full Moon Menyebarkan dan spin Bonus simbol pencar Gratis, untuk membuat kombinasi pemenang terbaik. Selain itu, garis menang dihasilkan dari kombinasi di mana Multiplier berpartisipasi simbol liar dikalikan dengan nilai yang ditampilkan pada simbol. Nilai multiplier diberikan adalah acak dan dapat dari x1 ke x5.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Catatan:</strong> Semua <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />simbol menghitung sampai nilai multiplier yang sama. Jika ada 2 atau lebih simbol-simbol tersebut, nilai-nilai multiplier mereka tidak ditambahkan. Sebagai contoh, jika pada payline menang ada 3 <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />simbol dengan x2 nilai multiplier, garis kemenangan hanya akan dikalikan dengan x2.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Catatan:</strong> Bila tidak menggantikan simbol lainnya, <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />simbol membayar sebagai dikalikan simbol Dr Blackwood.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Gratis spin Bonus Simbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>3, 4 atau 5 Gratis spin Bonus pencar simbol <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" />muncul secara bersamaan di manapun pada gulungan selama pemicu permainan utama fitur Free Spins.</p>\r\n<p>Informasi lebih lanjut tentang fitur Free Spins dapat ditemukan <a href="#">di sini</a> .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stacked Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simbol Naga Jewel <img src="../img/ashfmf_stacked.jpg" alt="" />ditumpuk pada semua gulungan. Ini berarti bahwa simbol Naga Jewel muncul satu di atas yang lain pada gulungan, sehingga membuat pembayaran yang lebih tinggi mungkin.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Fitur Bulan penuh</strong></p>\r\n<p>Fitur Full Moon dipicu ketika simbol Full Moon Menyebarkan <img src="../img/ashfmf_fullmoon.jpg" alt="" />muncul pada reel 5 selama permainan utama seperti yang dijelaskan di atas dalam <strong>Full Moon Tebar Symbol</strong> bagian.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a name="ashfmf_frees"></a>Spins Gratis</strong></p>\r\n<p>Fitur Free Spins akan memiliki nomor yang berbeda dari berputar bebas dan multiplier menang berbeda tergantung pada jumlah <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" />simbol yang telah memicu itu.</p>\r\n<table class="table"><colgroup><col width="250" /><col width="250" /><col width="250" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr><th><strong>Jumlah <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" />simbol <br />memicu Gratis Spins</strong></th><th><strong>Jumlah awal berputar bebas <br />diberikan</strong></th><th><strong>Nilai awal win multiplier <br />diberikan</strong></th></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n<td><center>1</center></td>\r\n<td><center>1</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>4</center></td>\r\n<td><center>2</center></td>\r\n<td><center>2</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>5</center></td>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Ketika Gratis Spins dipicu, Anda akan dibawa ke kuburan, di mana Anda harus memilih kuburan. Klik di kuburan untuk mengambilnya. Setiap akan penghargaan makam baik tambahan jumlah berputar bebas (dari 1 sampai 4), atau tambahan nilai menang multiplier (dari x1 ke x4), yang akan ditambahkan ke nilai awal yang telah Anda menang. Ketika kuburan Anda telah memilih mengungkapkan <strong>Collect</strong> , memetik diakhiri. Mengklik<strong>Lanjutkan</strong> pada layar yang muncul setelah itu dimulai Gratis Spins.</p>\r\n<p>The <strong>Gratis Spins</strong> kotak di sebelah kiri atas dari jendela permainan menunjukkan berputar bebas akumulasi Anda telah memenangkan. The<strong>Multiplier</strong> kotak di sebelah kanan atas dari jendela permainan menampilkan akumulasi kemenangan nilai multiplier. Nilai win multiplier tidak berubah setelah tahap memetik telah selesai. Semua kemenangan baris selama Gratis Spins dikalikan dengan nilai tersebut.</p>\r\n<p>Jumlah tertinggi berputar bebas Anda bisa menang sama sekali adalah 20. Nilai multiplier tertinggi adalah 5.</p>\r\n<p>Selama Gratis Spins semua <img src="../img/ashfmf_drblackwood.jpg" alt="" />simbol bertindak sebagai Multiplier Wilds, mengalikan baris menang hingga 25.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Catatan:</strong> pengganda Multiplier liar pra-dihitung untuk menjelaskan gratis berputar multiplier.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Selama Gratis Spins, gulungan yang berputar secara otomatis dengan menggunakan taruhan yang sama per baris seperti pada spin yang memenangkan fitur tersebut.</p>\r\n<p>Setelah setiap putaran, kemenangan untuk spin yang ditampilkan di <strong>Win</strong> bidang. The <strong>Gratis Spins Jumlah</strong> lapangan menunjukkan kemenangan akumulasi dari semua berputar bebas dimainkan sejauh ini. Jumlah berputar bebas tersisa ditampilkan dalam <strong>Gratis Spins</strong> kotak.</p>\r\n<p>Setelah semua Spins Gratis telah selesai layar muncul yang menunjukkan kemenangan akumulasi dari semua berputar bebas. Klik <strong>Lanjutkan</strong> untuk kembali ke gulungan permainan utama.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kembali ke Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>Teoritis persentase kembali ke pemain (RTP) adalah 94,01%.</p>', 'id'),
(24, '29', '<p><strong>5-reel khe c&#7855;m 20-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a khe Fortunes Full Moon l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p + v&agrave; - b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>d&ograve;ng Bet</strong> &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng ho&#7863;c gi&#7843;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c Full Moon Fortunes tr&ograve; ch&#417;i lu&ocirc;n ch&#417;i v&#7899;i 20 payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n. S&#7889; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n l&agrave; c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i tr&#7853;n v&ograve;ng b&#7857;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n. T&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong <strong>T&#7893;ng Bet</strong> h&#7897;p ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n <strong>Auto Play</strong> n&uacute;t.</li>\r\n<li>Di chu&#7897;t qua m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; chung ti&#7873;n ti&#7873;m n&#259;ng cho bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>spin</strong> quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873; v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i.</li>\r\n<li>Cu&#7897;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xoay s&#7869; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng Auto Play. <br />Click v&agrave;o <strong>Auto Play</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y ch&#7885;n. Ch&#7885;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&oacute;. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&#361;ng b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u c&aacute;c ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. Trong Auto Play, <strong>Auto Play</strong> n&uacute;t hi&#7875;n th&#7883; s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin c&ograve;n l&#7841;i. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh, khi b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; kinh ph&iacute; &#273;&#7875; quay ti&#7871;p theo, ho&#7863;c khi c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c quay t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7899;m b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n <strong>D&#7915;ng Auto Play</strong> , n&#7857;m &#8203;&#8203;&#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Turbo</strong> trong c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y ch&#7885;n Auto Play bi&#7871;n Ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Turbo ho&#7863;c t&#7855;t. Bi&#7871;n n&oacute; tr&ecirc;n t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; l&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng quay trong Auto Play.</li>\r\n<li>Th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo paytable. Gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; b&#7857;ng &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i gi&aacute; tr&#7883; t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable.C&aacute;c paytable c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang, tr&ecirc;n <strong>Ti&#7873;n chung</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>Tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ch&#7881; c&oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n. th&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n payline kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i hi&#7875;n th&#7883; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7897;ng d&#7891;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>trang th&ocirc;ng tin:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Info</strong> m&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>&lt;&lt;</strong> v&agrave; <strong>&gt;&gt;</strong> n&uacute;t &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cho ph&eacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&aacute;c nhau. M&#7897;t c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c &#273;&#7875; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh l&agrave; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o c&aacute;c n&uacute;t v&#7899;i t&ecirc;n trang &#7903; ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893;.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Ti&#7873;n chung</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng (c&aacute;c "paytable").</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Full Moon</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Full Moon.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch quy lu&#7853;t c&#7911;a n&oacute;.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Payline</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh minh h&#7885;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline c&oacute; th&#7875; v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c cho vi&#7879;c t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a h&#7885;.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>V&#7873; Reels</strong> tho&aacute;t ra kh&#7887;i m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh chi&#7871;u v&agrave; tr&#7843; l&#7841;i cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. T&#7845;t c&#7843; 20 payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c minh h&#7885;a tr&ecirc;n <strong>Payline</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7845;t c&#7843; 20 payline lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i. Ti&#7873;n chung th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable (tr&ecirc;n <strong>Ti&#7873;n chung</strong> trang) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; trong paytable tr&ecirc;n <strong>Ti&#7873;n chung</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n l&#7841;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Win H&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#7889;i &#273;a</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a trong game c&oacute; m&#7897;t gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n tr&ecirc;n. &#272;&#7875; bi&#7871;t th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng tin, xem c&aacute;c &#272;i&#7873;u kho&#7843;n v&agrave; &#272;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n ph&#7847;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>hoang d&atilde; Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild <img src="../img/ashfmf_wild.jpg" alt="" />c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; m&#7863;t tr&#259;ng Scatter &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; v&agrave; mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin th&#432;&#7903;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n thanh to&aacute;n ri&ecirc;ng cho 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&#432; &#273;&atilde; th&#7845;y trong paytable. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843; thay v&igrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n n&#7871;u s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; Wilds l&agrave; l&#7899;n h&#417;n so v&#7899;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n (trong chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng n&#417;i hoang d&atilde; &#273;ang &#273;&#7913;ng trong nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng kh&aacute;c).</p>\r\n<p><strong>Full Moon Scatter Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Full Moon Scatter <img src="../img/ashfmf_fullmoon.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n reel 5 trong ch&#7881; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh. Khi n&oacute; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n, t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Ti&#7871;n s&#297; Blackwood <img src="../img/ashfmf_drblackwood.jpg" alt="" />hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;n th&agrave;nh Multiplier bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng hoang d&atilde; <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Multiplier hoang d&atilde; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Multiplier hoang Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Multiplier hoang d&atilde; <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />c&oacute; th&#7875; thay th&#7871; cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; M&#7863;t tr&#259;ng Scatter &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; v&agrave; mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin th&#432;&#7903;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra, d&ograve;ng th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7915; m&#7897;t s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p trong &#273;&oacute; Multiplier tham Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; tr&ecirc;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. Gi&aacute; tr&#7883; nh&acirc;n trao t&#7863;ng l&agrave; ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7915; x1 &#273;&#7871;n x5.</p>\r\n<p><strong>L&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> T&#7845;t c&#7843; <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7871;m l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n gi&aacute; tr&#7883; nh&acirc;n gi&#7889;ng. N&#7871;u c&oacute; 2 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#432; v&#7853;y, gi&aacute; tr&#7883; nh&acirc;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n. V&iacute; d&#7909;, n&#7871;u tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; 3 <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng v&#7899;i m&#7897;t x2 gi&aacute; tr&#7883; nh&acirc;n, d&ograve;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng s&#7869; ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n x2.</p>\r\n<p><strong>L&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> Khi kh&ocirc;ng thay th&#7871; cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng kh&aacute;c, <img src="../img/ashfmf_multiwild.jpg" alt="" />nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#7843; ra nh&#432; nh&acirc;n hi&#7879;u Ti&#7871;n s&#297; Blackwood.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; Bonus Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>3, 4 ho&#7863;c 5 Mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin Bonus ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i &#7903; b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t ch&iacute;nh c&#7911;a t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p>Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y <a href="#">&#7903; &#273;&acirc;y</a> .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stacked Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng R&#7891;ng Jewel <img src="../img/ashfmf_stacked.jpg" alt="" />&#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&#7871;p ch&#7891;ng l&ecirc;n nhau tr&ecirc;n t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n phim. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; ngh&#297;a r&#7857;ng c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng R&#7891;ng Jewel xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n ch&#7891;ng l&ecirc;n nhau tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n, do &#273;&oacute; l&agrave;m cho th&#432;&#7903;ng cao nh&#7845;t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>T&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Full Moon</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Full Moon &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t khi bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Full Moon Scatter <img src="../img/ashfmf_fullmoon.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n reel 5 trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh nh&#432; &#273;&atilde; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch &#7903; tr&ecirc;n trong<strong>Full Moon Scatter Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng</strong> ph&#7847;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a name="ashfmf_frees"></a>quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; s&#7869; c&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; kh&aacute;c nhau c&#7911;a spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&agrave; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nh&acirc;n kh&aacute;c nhau t&ugrave;y thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng c&aacute;c <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" />bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng m&agrave; &#273;&atilde; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t n&oacute;.</p>\r\n<table class="table"><colgroup><col width="250" /><col width="250" /><col width="250" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr><th><strong>S&#7889; <img src="../img/ashfmf_bonus.jpg" alt="" />k&yacute; t&#7921; <br />k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin</strong></th><th><strong>S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng ban &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; <br />trao t&#7863;ng</strong></th><th><strong>Gi&aacute; tr&#7883; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nh&acirc;n ban &#273;&#7847;u <br />&#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao</strong></th></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n<td><center>1</center></td>\r\n<td><center>1</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>4</center></td>\r\n<td><center>2</center></td>\r\n<td><center>2</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center>5</center></td>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n<td><center>3</center></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Khi mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t ngh&#297;a trang, n&#417;i b&#7841;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i ch&#7885;n nh&#7919;ng ng&ocirc;i m&#7897;. Nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o m&#7897;t ng&ocirc;i m&#7897; &#273;&#7875; nh&#7863;t n&oacute;. M&#7895;i gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng m&#7897; ch&iacute; ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t s&#7889; b&#7893; sung c&#7911;a spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; (1-4), ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t gi&aacute; tr&#7883; th&#7855;ng th&#7847;u b&#7893; sung (t&#7915; x1 &#273;&#7871;n x4), m&agrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o c&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ban &#273;&#7847;u m&agrave; b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. Khi m&#7897;t ng&ocirc;i m&#7897; b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; ch&#7885;n cho th&#7845;y <strong>Thu</strong> , vi&#7879;c ch&#7885;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;m d&#7913;t. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Continue</strong> tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n sau &#273;&oacute; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c <strong>spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> h&#7897;p b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i cho c&aacute;c spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; t&iacute;ch l&#361;y b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. C&aacute;c <strong>Multiplier</strong> h&#7897;p ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i hi&#7875;n th&#7883; c&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; nh&acirc;n th&#7855;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y. C&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nh&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i sau khi giai &#273;o&#7841;n h&aacute;i xong. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng d&ograve;ng trong spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i gi&aacute; tr&#7883; &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p>S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng cao nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n l&agrave; 20. Gi&aacute; tr&#7883; nh&acirc;n cao nh&#7845;t l&agrave; 5.</p>\r\n<p>Trong th&#7901;i gian mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay t&#7845;t c&#7843; <img src="../img/ashfmf_drblackwood.jpg" alt="" />nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; Multiplier Wilds, nh&acirc;n d&ograve;ng th&#7855;ng l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 25.</p>\r\n<p><strong>L&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> Multiplier hoang d&atilde; nh&acirc;n l&agrave; t&iacute;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n cho mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay s&#7889; nh&acirc;n.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Trong th&#7901;i gian quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n xoay s&#7869; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; tr&ecirc;n m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng nh&#432; v&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c th&#7855;ng t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n<p>Sau m&#7895;i l&#7847;n quay, chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cho spin &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c. Vi&#7879;c <strong>mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin T&#7893;ng s&#7889;</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c hi&#7879;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7915; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; ch&#417;i cho &#273;&#7871;n nay. S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin mi&#7877