(29, 'DA', '<p>M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a b&#7841;n l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; d&#7921; &#273;o&aacute;n xem s&#7889; ti&#7871;p theo s&#7869; l&agrave; t&#7893;ng s&#7889; cao h&#417;n ho&#7863;c th&#7845;p h&#417;n so v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7899;c. &#272;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n, ch&#7885;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave; nh&#7845;n Start.B&acirc;y gi&#7901; c&aacute;c b&aacute;nh xe &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&eacute;o th&agrave;nh s&#7907;i v&agrave; sau khi b&aacute;nh xe d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i, b&#7841;n c&oacute; &#273;&#7875; d&#7921; &#273;o&aacute;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ti&#7871;p theo b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o th&#7845;p h&#417;n ho&#7863;c cao h&#417;n. Xin l&#432;u &yacute; r&#7857;ng c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t s&#7889; kh&ocirc;ng bao gi&#7901; &#273;&#7871;n hai l&#7847;n trong m&#7897;t h&agrave;ng. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c, b&#7841;n ti&#7871;n m&#7897;t b&#432;&#7899;c. S&aacute;u b&#432;&#7899;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n m&#7897;t c&#7845;p. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n sai, b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t cu&#7897;c &#273;&igrave;nh c&ocirc;ng. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; m&#7897;t b&agrave;n th&#7855;ng n&#7919;a v&agrave; ch&#7885;n kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&uacute;ng, tr&ograve; ch&#417;i k&#7871;t th&uacute;c v&agrave; b&#7841;n b&#7883; m&#7845;t ti&#7873;n. V&#432;&#417;n t&#7899;i s&#7921; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c c&#7911;a m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; x&oacute;a &#273;&igrave;nh c&ocirc;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i c&#7911;a b&#7841;n (n&#7871;u b&#7841;n c&oacute;). N&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; m&#7897;t cu&#7897;c &#273;&igrave;nh c&ocirc;ng v&agrave; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&#7871;t th&uacute;c c&#7911;a c&aacute;c c&#7845;p, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7883;nh:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<