(39, '8', '<p><strong>5-reel Slots 20-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Blade l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; (&#273;&#7891;ng xu gi&aacute; tr&#7883;) c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>B&#7845;m &#273;&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i</strong> n&uacute;t gi&aacute;o ph&aacute;i &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>C&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c line. Khi s&#7889; ti&#7873;n t&#7889;i &#273;a l&agrave; &#273;&#7841;t (10 xu c&#7911;a m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n), nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset c&#432;&#7907;c line &#273;&#7875; m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu.</li>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&#7897;t payline. Khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, nh&#7845;n n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset n&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng. Payline c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c n&uacute;t s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n ph&iacute;a c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng. L&#7921;a ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t payline cao bao g&#7891;m t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p qu&aacute;. V&iacute; d&#7909;, ch&#7885;n payline 6 c&#361;ng k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 5.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i tr&#7853;n v&ograve;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>spin</strong> quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873; v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i. Trong gu&#7891;ng quay c&#7911;a <strong>spin</strong> thay &#273;&#7893;i th&agrave;nh n&uacute;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> . Nh&#7845;p <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong>k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ho&#7841;t h&igrave;nh spin v&agrave; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin.</li>\r\n<li>Reels c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. Nh&#7845;p + ho&#7863;c &acirc; &euro; "tr&ecirc;n <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7885;n s&#7889; li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p c&#7911;a spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Auto Start</strong> quay gu&#7891;ng. C&aacute;c <strong>Auto Start</strong> n&uacute;t thay &#273;&#7893;i v&agrave;o <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> trong ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start c&#7911;a reelspin. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i, ho&#7863;c khi ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo paytable. D&ograve;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. Scatter th&#7855;ng = t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. C&aacute;c paytable c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ch&#7881; c&oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n khi th&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n payline kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y. Win ticker c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#7915;ng l&#7841;i b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c.</li>\r\n<li>th&#7855;ng payline v&agrave; t&#7893;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; tr&ecirc;n d&#7843;i n&#7857;m &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a cu&#7897;n ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Trang Th&ocirc;ng tin:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Info</strong> m&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau.Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#361;i t&ecirc;n &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cho ph&eacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c nhau.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. Khi m&#7903; ra sau khi m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng (s&#7889; k&yacute; hi&#7879;u v&agrave; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c s&#7889; nh&acirc;n) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&aacute;nh d&#7845;u v&agrave; ch&#7899;p m&#7855;t.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Blade Symbol Chia</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;ch t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng chia nh&#7887; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&#361;ng nh&#432; h&agrave;nh vi c&#7911;a n&oacute;.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Marvel Multi-Level B&iacute; &#7849;n Progressive Jackpot</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh v&agrave;o Marvel Multi-Level B&iacute; &#7849;n Progressive Jackpot tr&ograve; ch&#417;i m&agrave; th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t trong b&#7889;n gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch game&acirc; &euro; &trade; s quy t&#7855;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Hi&#7879;n Payline</strong> c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7845;p t&#7915; trang paytable &#273;&#7875; m&#7903; ra m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh minh h&#7885;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline c&oacute; th&#7875;. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Hide Payline</strong> &#273;&oacute;ng m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho <strong>paytable</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>l&#7841;i</strong> tho&aacute;t ra kh&#7887;i <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p<strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; cho quy t&#7855;c n&agrave;y. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;u v&ograve;ng. To&aacute;n t&#7927; l&#7879; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line. M&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; l&agrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter, m&agrave; chung ti&#7873;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n l&#7841;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y. <strong>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i l&agrave; c&aacute;c <img src="../img/blade_sym0.jpg" alt="" />bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. N&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, tr&#7915; Scatter <img src="../img/blade_sym12.jpg" alt="" />v&agrave; Split <img src="../img/blade_sym11.jpg" alt="" />, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra, hai hay nhi&#7873;u k&yacute; hi&#7879;u hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline tr&#7843; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng theo c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c c&#7911;a paytable.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; payline c&#7909; th&#7875;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; ba ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter trong k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin, m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&ecirc;m l&agrave; ki&#7871;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. Vi&#7879;c thanh to&aacute;n cho nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, b&#7845;t k&#7875; v&#7883; tr&iacute;, 15 Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng v&#7899;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n (xem d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y). Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter c&#361;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; nh&#432; m&#7897;t hoang t&#7855;m v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; cho c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Split v&agrave; Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&aacute;c t&#7915; &acirc; &euro; ~EXTRA Wilda &euro; &trade; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u ba ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng khi ch&#417;i Free, ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao t&#7863;ng h&#417;n 15 tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chia</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Chia s&#7869; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n th&#7913; 5 sau khi m&#7897;t spin, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng trong b&#7845;t k&#7923; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia th&agrave;nh hai v&agrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh l&agrave; hai bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng gi&#7889;ng h&#7879;t nhau. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&#7853;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t qu&#7843; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7911;a s&aacute;u l&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875;. Chung ti&#7873;n cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7911;a s&aacute;u l&agrave; chi ti&#7871;t trong paytable.</p>\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Split l&agrave; c&oacute; s&#7861;n trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#7915; Scatter c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia khi thay th&#7871; nh&#432; t&#7855;m Wild.</p>\r\n<p><strong>C&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. &#272;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i ph&#7843;i b&#7845;m v&agrave;o <strong>Click to Start</strong> . M&#7897;t khi ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n, c&#7845;p cho ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n ban &#273;&#7847;u ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a X2, X3, X4 ho&#7863;c X5. M&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; b&#7845;t k&#7923; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; &#273;&oacute;. M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, sau &#273;&oacute; quay t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n<p>Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&#432;&#7907;c line, k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu v&agrave; s&#7889; d&ograve;ng l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng ch&#417;i.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; c&oacute; b&#432;&#7899;c nh&acirc;n c&#7911;a X2, X3, X4 v&agrave; X5. N&#7871;u ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i th&#7855;ng sau m&#7897;t spin, s&#7889; nh&acirc;n t&#259;ng l&ecirc;n m&#7897;t b&#432;&#7899;c (X5 l&agrave; cao nh&#7845;t) v&agrave; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; &#273;&oacute;. N&#7871;u kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau m&#7897;t spin, s&#7889; nh&acirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;m &#273;i m&#7897;t b&#432;&#7899;c (X2 l&agrave; th&#7845;p nh&#7845;t). C&aacute;c d&ograve;ng kh&aacute;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i, c&#417; h&#7897;i l&#7899;n h&#417;n ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i c&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; gia t&#259;ng s&#7889; nh&acirc;n. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter c&#361;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; nh&#432; m&#7897;t hoang t&#7855;m, thay th&#7871; t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#7915; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Split v&agrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild.</p>\r\n<p>V&agrave;o cu&#7889;i c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t chi ti&#7871;t c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng th&#7855;ng xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n. &#272;&#7875; tr&#7903; l&#7841;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c</strong> .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot l&agrave; m&#7897;t &#273;a c&#7845;p ti&#7871;n b&#7897; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i jackpot m&agrave; c&oacute; s&#7861;n trong t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&#7899;i t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel.M&#7897;t t&#7927; l&#7879; nh&#7887; c&#7911;a m&#7895;i c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel, b&#7903;i m&#7895;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y trong m&#7895;i nhi&#7873;u s&ograve;ng b&#7841;c tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o jackpot l&#361;y ti&#7871;n.</p>\r\n<p>Vi&#7879;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&agrave; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot l&agrave; ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; x&#7843;y ra sau khi b&#7845;t k&#7923; quay trong b&#7845;t k&#7923; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t. N&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; do b&#7845;t k&#7923; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&agrave; th&#7853;m ch&iacute; m&#7897;t spin m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;i&#7873;u g&igrave; trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; v&#7853;y, b&#7845;t k&#7923; c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot.Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c&#417; h&#7897;i k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i t&#259;ng Jackpot ho&#7863;c gi&#7843;m t&#7927; l&#7879; thu&#7853;n v&#7899;i m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c. B&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a m&#7897;t trong b&#7889;n gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t. Ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot ti&#7871;t l&#7897; jackpot &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao cho b&#7841;n, nh&#432;ng kh&ocirc;ng x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh n&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p>C&oacute; b&#7889;n c&#7845;p &#273;&#7897; kh&aacute;c nhau c&#7911;a gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t m&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng: Power Jackpot, Extra Power Jackpot, Super Power Jackpot v&agrave; Ultimate &#273;i&#7879;n Jackpot. C&aacute;c lo&#7841;i kh&aacute;c nhau c&#7911;a gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t n&#7855;m gi&#7919; m&#7897;t l&#432;&#7907;ng gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng kh&aacute;c nhau. C&aacute;c gamescreen jackpot ch&#7913;a 20 h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng m&agrave; trong &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i &#273;ang b&#7883; &#273;&#7843;o l&#7897;n. Nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o m&#7897;t h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng s&#7869; bi&#7871;n n&oacute; xung quanh v&agrave; ti&#7871;t l&#7897; m&#7897;t trong b&#7889;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&#7855;c &#7903; ph&iacute;a b&ecirc;n kia. M&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; t&igrave;m th&#7845;y ba bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p, b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng trong jackpot t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng v&#7899;i c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y. Tr&uacute;ng th&#432;&#7903;ng Jackpot &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o th&#7855;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh (n&#7871;u c&oacute;) v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; th&#7855;ng kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot tr&ograve; ch&#417;i c&oacute; m&#7897;t gi&#7901; th&#7901;i gian ch&#7901;. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; ngh&#297;a r&#7857;ng n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng trong m&#7897;t kho&#7843;ng th&#7901;i gian, b&#7841;n s&#7869; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p>\r\n<p>The Jackpot cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Seed</strong> (bao nhi&ecirc;u ti&#7873;n c&#7911;a Gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&#7899;i):</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled">\r\n<li>Power: 50 &euro;</li>\r\n<li>Extra Power: 500 &euro;</li>\r\n<li>Super Power: 5000 &euro;</li>\r\n<li>Cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng Power: 100.000 &euro;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>T&#7927; l&#7879; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p</strong> (t&#7927; l&#7879; ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m c&#7911;a m&#7895;i c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i v&agrave;o Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>0.99%</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Win &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n</strong> (c&aacute;c k&#7871;t qu&#7843; m&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&aacute;c Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>B&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o tr&ograve; ch&#417;i jackpot &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. c&aacute;c k&yacute; hi&#7879;u Match 3 jackpot c&#7911;a Jackpot t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng ho&#7863;c ch&#7901; &#273;&#7907;i cho b&#7897; &#273;&#7871;m th&#7901;i gian ch&#7841;y ra ngo&agrave;i.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u Win</strong> (nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; b&#7841;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i l&agrave;m g&igrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n cho c&aacute;c Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>Ch&#417;i m&#7897;t tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; gi&#7889;ng v&agrave; Jackpot l&agrave; &#273;&#7891;ng Euro trong m&#7841;ng ti&#7871;n b&#7897; v&agrave; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a h&#7885; trong ti&#7873;n t&#7879; &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n l&agrave; ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o t&#7927; gi&aacute; h&#7889;i &#273;o&aacute;i.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c c&#417; ch&#7871; c&#7911;a Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot c&#7845;m th&#7855;ng jackpot &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i.</li>\r\n<li>Kh&ocirc;ng ho&agrave;n h&#7843;o trong k&#7871;t n&#7889;i Internet c&oacute; th&#7875; g&acirc;y ra c&aacute;c b&#7841;n tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m s&#7921; ch&#7853;m tr&#7877; trong c&aacute;c tin nh&#7855;n Jackpot ho&#7863;c c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t, nh&#432;ng h&#7885; kh&ocirc;ng &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; Jackpot th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; c&#7847;u th&#7911;</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&#7927; l&#7879; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i (RTP) l&agrave; 95.05%.</p>', 'vn');
