(42, '9', '<p><strong>5-reel 50-line slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>The object of Blade 50 Lines is to obtain a winning symbol combination by spinning the reels.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To play the game:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A wagering denomination (coin value) can be chosen by clicking the <strong>Click to Change</strong> denomination button in the lower left-hand corner of the screen.</li>\r\n<li>Line bets are chosen by clicking <strong>Bet per Line</strong>. Each click adds a coin to the line bet. When the maximum amount is reached (10 coins of the selected wagering denomination), clicking the button again resets the line bet to one coin.</li>\r\n<li>Paylines are chosen by clicking <strong>Lines</strong>. Each click activates more paylines in steps of multiples of 5, starting with 1 (1, 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40, 45, 50). When all paylines are activated, clicking the button again resets it to one active payline.</li>\r\n<li>Total bet per game round = line bet X active paylines.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Spin</strong> spins the reels with the current selection of lines and line bets. During the reel spin the <strong>Spin</strong> button changes into<strong>Stop</strong>. Clicking<strong>Stop</strong> ends the spin animation and immediately displays the spin result.</li>\r\n<li>Reels can also be spun using the <strong>Auto Start</strong> function. Clicking + or &ndash; above <strong>Auto Start</strong> selects the number of spins to be played automatically. Clicking <strong>Auto Start</strong> spins the reels. The <strong>Auto Start</strong> button changes into <strong>Stop</strong> during the Auto Start mode. The Auto Start mode ends when the reels have been spun the number of times determined by the player, or when the player clicks <strong>Stop</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking the <strong>Turbo Mode</strong> button switches on or off the Turbo Mode thus turning on or off some of the win animations and sounds, and making the reels spin faster or slower.</li>\r\n<li>Wins are calculated according to the paytable. Line win = line bet X corresponding multiplier according to the paytable. Scatter win = total bet X corresponding multiplier according to the paytable. The paytable can be accessed via the <strong>Info</strong> page.</li>\r\n<li>On a given payline, only the highest payline winning combination pays while simultaneous winnings on different paylines are accumulated.</li>\r\n<li>In the case of a winning spin, the <strong>Win</strong> field displays the accumulating winnings. The Win ticker can be stopped by clicking anywhere on the screen to display the total win amount immediately.</li>\r\n<li>Payline wins and the total win are also displayed on the strip located at the bottom of the reels or the game window.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Info page:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Info</strong> opens the reference screen describing different game components. Clicking the arrow buttons at the lower right-hand corner of the screen enables navigating between the different info screens.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paytable</strong> screen shows all winning combinations. When opened after a winning spin, the winning symbol combinations (number of symbols and bet multiplier) are highlighted and blink.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Free Games</strong> screen describes the symbol combinations necessary to trigger the Free Games feature and describes the Free Games feature rules.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Blade Symbol Split</strong> screen explains how the split feature is triggered as well as its behavior.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Marvel Multi-Level Mystery Progressive Jackpot</strong> screen describes how to win entry to the Marvel Multi-Level Mystery Progressive Jackpot game that wins one of 4 jackpots, and explains the rules of the game.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Show Paylines</strong> opens a screen that illustrates all possible payline combinations. Clicking <strong>Hide Paylines</strong> closes this screen and returns to the <strong>Info</strong> screen.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Back</strong> exits the <strong>Info</strong> screen and returns to the game.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Active paylines are represented by lines that appear over the reels. Paylines can be activated and their shape displayed by progressively clicking <strong>Lines</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Only active paylines can register wins.</li>\r\n<li>There is a difference between the line bet and the total bet. The line bet shows how much is being bet on a single payline. The total bet shows how much is being bet in total on the game round. Payouts shown in the paytable are multiplied by the line bet.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Scatter symbol is an exception to these rules. More information about the Scatter symbol can be found below. <strong>About payouts:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payouts are listed on the <strong>Paytable</strong> screen. To find the possible win amount, the line bet must be multiplied by the payout.</li>\r\n<li>If two payline winning combinations occur on the same line, the higher of them is paid out. If more than one active payline has a winning combination, the winnings are accumulated.</li>\r\n<li>Winning combinations must start from the leftmost reel, and the symbols have to be on consecutive reels.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Scatter symbol is an exception to these rules. More information about the Scatter symbol can be found below. <strong>Wild symbols</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Wild symbol in the game is the <img src="../img/blade_sym0.jpg" alt="" /> symbol. It can stand for any other symbol, except Scatter <img src="../img/blade_sym12.jpg" alt="" /> and Split <img src="../img/blade_sym11.jpg" alt="" />, to make the best possible winning combination.</p>\r\n<p>There is also a separate payout for 2 or more Wild symbols on an active payline, as seen in the Paytable. This is paid out instead of the regular symbol win if the win amount from Wild is larger than the win from the regular symbols (by Wild standing in).</p>\r\n<p><strong>Scatter symbols</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Scatter symbols do not have to occur on a particular payline. If there are 3 or more Scatter symbols in the spin results, the payout earned is multiplied by the total bet and added to payline winnings. The payout for the Scatter symbols is multiplied by the total bet. If 3 or more Scatter symbols appear on the reels simultaneously, regardless of position, 15 Free Games are awarded with a dynamic multiplier (see below). In Free Games, the Scatter symbol also serves as an Extra Wild and can stand for any other symbol, except for the Split symbol and the Wild symbol, to make the best possible winning combination. In Free Games, the words ''EXTRA WILD'' appear on the symbol.</p>\r\n<p>If 3 or more Scatter symbols appear anywhere on the reels during Free Games, the player is awarded 15 more Free Games.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Split symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>If the Split symbol appears on the 5th reel after a spin, the last symbol in any winning combination will be split into 2 and will count as 2 identical symbols. All resulting wins will be paid. This means that combinations of 6 are possible. The payouts for the combinations of 6 are detailed in the paytable.</p>\r\n<p>The Split feature is available in the main game and in Free Games. In the main game, all symbols except Scatter can be split. In Free Games, the Scatter symbol can be split when substituting as Extra Wild.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Free Games</strong></p>\r\n<p>3 or more Scatter symbols trigger the Free Games. To begin, the player must click on <strong>Click to Start</strong>. Once the player clicks to start, a screen appears, granting the player a random initial multiplier of X2, X3, X4 or X5. A multiplier means that any win is multiplied by that number. The screen changes automatically to the Free Game reels, which then spin automatically.</p>\r\n<p>During the Free Games, the line bet, coin size and number of lines are those last played.</p>\r\n<p>The Free Games have multiplier steps of X2, X3, X4 and X5. If the player wins after a spin, the multiplier is increased by one step (X5 being the highest) and the wins are multiplied by that number. If there is no win after a spin, the multiplier decreases by one step (X2 being the lowest). The more lines are played, the greater chances the player has of a multiplier increase. During the Free Games, the Scatter symbol serves also as an Extra Wild, replacing all symbols except for the Split symbol and the Wild symbol.</p>\r\n<p>At the end of the Free Games, a special screen detailing the feature wins appears. To return to the main game, click <strong>Continue</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Marvel Mystery Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>Marvel Mystery Jackpot is a multi-level progressive jackpot game that is available in all Marvel games and is linked to all Marvel games. A small percentage of each bet in the Marvel games, by every person playing this game in each of many online casinos, is added to the progressive jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>The trigger that starts the Jackpot game is random and can occur after any spin in any of the linked games. It is not caused by any symbol combination in the linked games and even a spin that does not win anything in the main game can trigger the Jackpot game. Likewise, any bet with any size in the linked games can trigger the Jackpot game. Nonetheless, the chances of triggering the Jackpot game increase or decrease proportionally to the bet size. Entering the Jackpot game guarantees a win of one of the four jackpots. Playing the Jackpot game reveals the jackpot that has been awarded to you, but does not determine it.</p>\r\n<p>There are four different levels of jackpots that you can win: Power Jackpot, Extra Power Jackpot, Super Power Jackpot and Ultimate Power Jackpot. Different types of jackpots hold different prize amounts. The jackpot gamescreen contains 20 squares which in the beginning of the gameplay are turned upside down. Clicking on a square will turn it around and reveal one of four jackpot symbols on the other side. Once you have found three matching symbols, you win the jackpot that corresponds to these symbols. Jackpot winnings are added to the main game winnings (if any) and are displayed in the <strong>Win</strong> field together with any other winnings.</p>\r\n<p>The Marvel Mystery Jackpot game has a timeout timer. This means that if you do not pick a square in a set amount of time, you will automatically receive your prize. The Jackpot for this game works like this:</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Seed</strong> (how much money the Jackpots start out with):</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled">\r\n<li>Power: &euro;50</li>\r\n<li>Extra Power: &euro;500</li>\r\n<li>Super Power: &euro;5,000</li>\r\n<li>Ultimate Power: &euro;100,000</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Contribution rate</strong> (what percentage of each bet goes into Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>0.99%</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Win condition</strong> (the result you have to get to win the Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>Entering the jackpot game guarantees a win. Match 3 jackpot symbols of the corresponding Jackpot or wait for the timer to run out.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Win requirements</strong> (what you need to do to be eligible for the Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>Play a Marvel game.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The seed and Jackpot values are in Euros in the progressive network and their value in your local currency is dependent on the currency exchange rate.</li>\r\n<li>The mechanics of Marvel Mystery Jackpot prohibit simultaneous jackpot winnings.</li>\r\n<li>Imperfections in the Internet connectivity may cause you to experience delays in Jackpot messages or updates, but they do not affect actual Jackpot wins.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>The theoretical percentage return to player (RTP) is 91.98%.</p>', 'en'),
(43, '9', '<p><strong>5-reel slot 50-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>Objek Blade 50 Garis adalah untuk mendapatkan kombinasi simbol menang dengan memutar reel.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Untuk memainkan permainan:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sebuah denominasi Taruhan (nilai mata uang) dapat dipilih dengan mengklik <strong>Klik untuk Mengubah</strong> tombol denominasi di sudut kiri bawah layar.</li>\r\n<li>Taruhan baris yang dipilih dengan mengklik <strong>Bet per baris</strong> . Setiap klik menambahkan koin dengan taruhan baris. Ketika jumlah maksimum tercapai (10 koin dari denominasi Taruhan dipilih), klik tombol lagi taruhan baris untuk satu koin.</li>\r\n<li>Paylines yang dipilih dengan mengklik <strong>baris</strong> . Setiap klik mengaktifkan lebih paylines dalam langkah kelipatan 5, dimulai dengan 1 (1, 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40, 45, 50). Ketika semua paylines diaktifkan, klik lagi tombol reset ke satu payline aktif.</li>\r\n<li>Total taruhan per game putaran = taruhan garis X paylines aktif.</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>spin</strong> berputar gulungan dengan pilihan saat ini dari garis dan garis taruhan. Selama reel spin <strong>spin</strong> tombol berubah menjadi <strong>Berhenti</strong>. Mengklik <strong>Berhenti</strong> mengakhiri animasi berputar dan langsung menampilkan hasil spin.</li>\r\n<li>Gulungan juga dapat berputar menggunakan <strong>Auto Start</strong> fungsi. Mengklik + atau - di atas <strong>Auto Start</strong> akan memilih jumlah berputar untuk dimainkan secara otomatis. Mengklik <strong>Auto Start</strong> berputar gulungan. The <strong>Auto Start</strong> tombol berubah menjadi <strong>Berhenti</strong> selama modus Auto Start. Modus Auto Start berakhir ketika gulungan telah berputar jumlah kali ditentukan oleh pemain, atau saat pemain mengklik <strong>Berhenti</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Turbo Mode</strong> tombol switch atau menonaktifkan Turbo Mode sehingga menyalakan atau mematikan beberapa animasi menang dan suara, dan membuat gulungan berputar lebih cepat atau lebih lambat.</li>\r\n<li>Menang dihitung berdasarkan paytable tersebut. Garis menang taruhan garis X = multiplier yang sesuai menurut paytable. Pencar win = total taruhan X multiplier yang sesuai menurut paytable. Paytable dapat diakses melalui <strong>Info</strong> halaman.</li>\r\n<li>Pada payline diberikan, hanya tertinggi kombinasi payline menang membayar sementara kemenangan simultan pada paylines yang berbeda diakumulasi.</li>\r\n<li>Dalam kasus spin menang, <strong>Win</strong> bidang menampilkan kemenangan terakumulasi. Win ticker dapat dihentikan dengan mengklik di manapun pada layar untuk menampilkan jumlah total menang segera.</li>\r\n<li>menang payline dan menang total juga ditampilkan pada strip yang terletak di bagian bawah gulungan atau jendela permainan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Halaman Info:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Info</strong> membuka layar referensi yang menggambarkan komponen permainan yang berbeda.Mengklik tombol panah di sudut kanan bawah layar memungkinkan navigasi antara layar berbagai info.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paytable</strong> layar menunjukkan semua kombinasi pemenang. Ketika dibuka setelah spin menang, kombinasi simbol pemenang (jumlah simbol dan multiplier taruhan) yang disorot dan berkedip.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Free Games</strong> layar menggambarkan kombinasi simbol yang diperlukan untuk memicu fitur Free Games dan menjelaskan Free Games aturan fitur.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Pisau Simbol Berpisah</strong> layar menjelaskan bagaimana fitur split dipicu serta perilakunya.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Marvel Multi-Level Misteri Progressive Jackpot</strong> layar menjelaskan cara untuk memenangkan masuk ke Marvel Multi-Level Misteri Progressive Jackpot permainan yang menang salah satu dari 4 jackpot, dan menjelaskan aturan permainan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>paylines Tampilkan</strong> membuka layar yang menggambarkan semua kombinasi payline mungkin. Mengklik <strong>Hide Paylines</strong> menutup layar ini dan kembali ke <strong>Info</strong> layar.</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Kembali</strong> keluar dari <strong>Info</strong> layar dan kembali ke permainan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Paylines aktif diwakili oleh garis-garis yang muncul di atas gulungan. Paylines dapat diaktifkan dan bentuk mereka ditampilkan dengan mengklik <strong>Garis</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Hanya paylines aktif dapat mendaftar menang.</li>\r\n<li>Ada perbedaan antara garis taruhan dan total taruhan. Taruhan garis menunjukkan berapa banyak yang bertaruh pada payline tunggal. Total taruhan menunjukkan berapa banyak yang bertaruh secara total pada putaran permainan. Pembayaran ditampilkan dalam paytable dikalikan dengan taruhan baris.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Simbol Scatter merupakan pengecualian aturan ini. Informasi lebih lanjut tentang simbol Scatter dapat ditemukan di bawah. <strong>Tentang pembayaran:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pembayaran tercatat di <strong>Paytable</strong> layar. Untuk menemukan jumlah menang mungkin, garis taruhan harus dikalikan dengan payout.</li>\r\n<li>Jika dua kombinasi pemenang payline terjadi pada baris yang sama, lebih tinggi dari mereka dibayarkan. Jika lebih dari satu payline aktif memiliki kombinasi menang, kemenangan diakumulasikan.</li>\r\n<li>Kombinasi pemenang harus mulai dari gulungan paling kiri, dan simbol harus pada gulungan berturut-turut.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Simbol Scatter merupakan pengecualian aturan ini. Informasi lebih lanjut tentang simbol Scatter dapat ditemukan di bawah. <strong>Simbol Liar</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simbol liar dalam permainan adalah <img src="../img/blade_sym0.jpg" alt="" />simbol. Hal ini dapat berdiri untuk setiap simbol lain, kecuali scatter <img src="../img/blade_sym12.jpg" alt="" />dan Split <img src="../img/blade_sym11.jpg" alt="" />, untuk membuat kombinasi pemenang terbaik.</p>\r\n<p>Ada juga pembayaran terpisah untuk 2 atau lebih simbol Wild pada payline aktif, seperti yang terlihat di Paytable tersebut. Ini dibayarkan bukan kemenangan simbol biasa jika jumlah menang dari Wild lebih besar daripada menang dari simbol biasa (dengan berdiri Liar di).</p>\r\n<p><strong>simbol scatter</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simbol Scatter tidak harus terjadi pada payline tertentu. Jika ada 3 atau lebih simbol Scatter dalam hasil spin, pembayaran yang diterima dikalikan dengan total taruhan dan ditambahkan ke payline kemenangan. Payout untuk simbol Scatter dikalikan dengan total taruhan. Jika 3 atau lebih simbol Scatter muncul pada gulungan secara bersamaan, terlepas dari posisi, 15 Free Games diberikan dengan multiplier yang dinamis (lihat di bawah).Dalam Game Gratis, simbol Menyebarkan juga berfungsi sebagai liar ekstra dan dapat berdiri untuk setiap simbol lain, kecuali simbol Split dan simbol liar, untuk membuat kombinasi pemenang terbaik. Dalam Game Gratis, kata-kata ''WILD EXTRA'' muncul pada simbol.</p>\r\n<p>Jika 3 atau lebih simbol Scatter muncul di manapun pada gulungan selama Game Gratis, pemain diberikan 15 lebih Game Gratis.</p>\r\n<p><strong>simbol perpecahan</strong></p>\r\n<p>Jika simbol Berpisah muncul pada reel 5 setelah spin, simbol terakhir di setiap kombinasi pemenang akan dibagi menjadi 2 dan akan dihitung sebagai 2 simbol identik. Semua kemenangan dihasilkan akan dibayar. Ini berarti bahwa kombinasi dari 6 yang mungkin. Pembayaran untuk kombinasi dari 6 yang rinci dalam paytable.</p>\r\n<p>Fitur Berpisah tersedia dalam permainan utama dan di Free Games. Dalam permainan utama, semua simbol kecuali Menyebarkan dapat dibagi.Dalam Game Gratis, simbol Menyebarkan dapat dibagi ketika mengganti sebagai Extra liar.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Permainan gratis</strong></p>\r\n<p>3 atau lebih simbol Scatter memicu Game Gratis. Untuk memulai, pemain harus mengklik <strong>Click to Start</strong> . Setelah pemain mengklik untuk memulai, layar muncul, pemberian pemain pengali awal acak X2, X3, X4 atau X5. Sebuah multiplier berarti menang setiap dikalikan dengan jumlah itu. Layar berubah secara otomatis ke gulungan permainan gratis, yang kemudian berputar secara otomatis.</p>\r\n<p>Selama Game Gratis, taruhan baris, koin ukuran dan jumlah baris adalah mereka terakhir bermain.</p>\r\n<p>The Free Games memiliki langkah-langkah multiplier X2, X3, X4 dan X5. Jika pemain menang setelah spin, multiplier meningkat dengan satu langkah (X5 yang tertinggi) dan menang dikalikan dengan jumlah itu. Jika tidak ada menang setelah spin, multiplier berkurang satu langkah (X2 yang terendah). Semakin banyak baris yang dimainkan, kemungkinan besar pemain memiliki kenaikan multiplier. Selama Game Gratis, simbol Menyebarkan berfungsi juga sebagai Liar Ekstra, mengganti semua simbol kecuali simbol Split dan simbol liar.</p>\r\n<p>Pada akhir Game Gratis, layar khusus merinci fitur menang muncul. Untuk kembali ke permainan utama, klik <strong>Lanjutkan</strong> .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Marvel Mystery Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>Marvel Mystery Jackpot adalah multi-level progresif jackpot permainan yang tersedia di semua game Marvel dan terkait dengan semua game Marvel. Sebagian kecil masing-masing taruhan dalam permainan Marvel, oleh setiap orang memainkan game ini di masing-masing banyak kasino online, ditambahkan ke jackpot progresif.</p>\r\n<p>Pemicu yang dimulai permainan Jackpot adalah acak dan dapat terjadi setelah satu putaran di salah satu permainan terkait. Hal ini tidak disebabkan oleh kombinasi simbol dalam game terkait dan bahkan spin yang tidak memenangkan apapun dalam permainan utama dapat memicu permainan Jackpot. Demikian juga, setiap taruhan dengan ukuran dalam permainan terkait dapat memicu permainan Jackpot. Meskipun demikian, kemungkinan memicu Jackpot peningkatan permainan atau menurun secara proporsional dengan ukuran taruhan. Memasuki game Jackpot menjamin kemenangan dari salah satu dari empat jackpot. Bermain game Jackpot mengungkapkan jackpot yang telah diberikan kepada Anda, tetapi tidak menentukan itu.</p>\r\n<p>Ada empat tingkatan yang berbeda dari jackpot yang dapat Anda menang: Daya Jackpot, Extra Power Jackpot, Super Power Jackpot dan Ultimate Power Jackpot. Berbagai jenis jackpot terus dalam jumlah hadiah yang berbeda. Jackpot gamescreen berisi 20 kotak yang pada awal gameplay yang terbalik. Klik di alun-alun akan memutarnya dan mengungkapkan salah satu dari empat simbol jackpot di sisi lain. Setelah Anda telah menemukan tiga simbol yang cocok, Anda menang jackpot yang sesuai dengan simbol-simbol ini. Kemenangan jackpot ditambahkan ke kemenangan permainan utama (jika ada) dan ditampilkan di <strong>Win</strong> bidang bersama dengan kemenangan lainnya.</p>\r\n<p>Marvel Mystery Jackpot permainan memiliki timer timeout. Ini berarti bahwa jika Anda tidak memilih persegi dalam waktu yang telah ditentukan, secara otomatis Anda akan menerima hadiah Anda. Jackpot untuk permainan ini bekerja seperti ini:</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Benih</strong> (berapa banyak uang jackpot mulai dengan):</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled">\r\n<li>Power: 50 &euro;</li>\r\n<li>Extra Power: 500 &euro;</li>\r\n<li>Super Power: &euro; 5,000</li>\r\n<li>Ultimate Power: &euro; 100,000</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Tingkat kontribusi</strong> (persentase masing-masing taruhan masuk ke Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>0.99%</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Kondisi Win</strong> (hasil Anda harus mendapatkan untuk memenangkan Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>Memasuki game jackpot menjamin kemenangan. simbol pertandingan 3 jackpot dari yang sesuai Jackpot atau menunggu timer habis.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Persyaratan Win</strong> (apa yang harus Anda lakukan untuk memenuhi persyaratan untuk Jackpot):</td>\r\n<td>Bermain game Marvel.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Tolong dicatat:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nilai-nilai benih dan Jackpot berada di Euro dalam jaringan progresif dan nilai mereka dalam mata uang lokal Anda tergantung pada nilai tukar mata uang.</li>\r\n<li>Mekanisme Marvel Mystery Jackpot melarang kemenangan jackpot simultan.</li>\r\n<li>Ketidaksempurnaan dalam konektivitas internet dapat menyebabkan Anda mengalami keterlambatan dalam pesan Jackpot atau update, tapi mereka tidak mempengaruhi yang sebenarnya Jackpot menang.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Kembali ke Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>Teoritis persentase kembali ke pemain (RTP) adalah 91,98%.</p>', 'id'),
(44, '9', '<p><strong>5-reel khe c&#7855;m 50-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Blade 50 Lines l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; (&#273;&#7891;ng xu gi&aacute; tr&#7883;) c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>B&#7845;m &#273;&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i</strong> n&uacute;t gi&aacute;o ph&aacute;i &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>C&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c line. Khi s&#7889; ti&#7873;n t&#7889;i &#273;a l&agrave; &#273;&#7841;t (10 xu c&#7911;a m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n), nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset c&#432;&#7907;c line &#273;&#7875; m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu.</li>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p ho&#7841;t h&#417;n payline trong c&aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c c&#7911;a b&#7897;i s&#7889; c&#7911;a 5, b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; 1 (1, 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40, 45, 50). Khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, nh&#7845;n n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset n&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i tr&#7853;n v&ograve;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>spin</strong> quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873; v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i. Trong gu&#7891;ng quay <strong>spin</strong> thay &#273;&#7893;i th&agrave;nh n&uacute;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> . Nh&#7845;p <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ho&#7841;t h&igrave;nh spin v&agrave; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin.</li>\r\n<li>Reels c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. Nh&#7845;p + ho&#7863;c - tr&ecirc;n <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7885;n s&#7889; spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.Nh&#7845;p <strong>Auto Start</strong> quay gu&#7891;ng. C&aacute;c <strong>Auto Start</strong> n&uacute;t thay &#273;&#7893;i v&agrave;o <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> trong ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i, ho&#7863;c khi ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Turbo Mode</strong> n&uacute;t c&ocirc;ng t&#7855;c ho&#7863;c t&#7855;t do &#273;&oacute; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Turbo b&#7853;t ho&#7863;c t&#7855;t m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh &#273;&#7897;ng v&agrave; &acirc;m thanh gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, v&agrave; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n quay nhanh h&#417;n ho&#7863;c ch&#7853;m h&#417;n.</li>\r\n<li>Th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo paytable. D&ograve;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. Scatter th&#7855;ng = t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. C&aacute;c paytable c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ch&#7881; c&oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n khi th&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n payline kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y. Win ticker c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#7915;ng l&#7841;i b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c.</li>\r\n<li>th&#7855;ng payline v&agrave; t&#7893;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; tr&ecirc;n d&#7843;i n&#7857;m &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a cu&#7897;n ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Trang Th&ocirc;ng tin:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Info</strong> m&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau.Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#361;i t&ecirc;n &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cho ph&eacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c nhau.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. Khi m&#7903; ra sau khi m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng (s&#7889; k&yacute; hi&#7879;u v&agrave; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c s&#7889; nh&acirc;n) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&aacute;nh d&#7845;u v&agrave; ch&#7899;p m&#7855;t.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Blade Symbol Chia</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;ch t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng chia nh&#7887; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&#361;ng nh&#432; h&agrave;nh vi c&#7911;a n&oacute;.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Marvel Multi-Level B&iacute; &#7849;n Progressive Jackpot</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh v&agrave;o Marvel Multi-Level B&iacute; &#7849;n Progressive Jackpot tr&ograve; ch&#417;i m&agrave; th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t trong 4 gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Hi&#7879;n Payline</strong> s&#7869; m&#7903; ra m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; minh h&#7885;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline c&oacute; th&#7875;. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Hide Payline</strong> &#273;&oacute;ng m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>l&#7841;i</strong> tho&aacute;t ra kh&#7887;i <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p<strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i. Ti&#7873;n chung th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y. <strong>V&#7873; Payouts:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; gu&#7891;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i. <strong>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng hoang d&atilde;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i l&agrave; c&aacute;c <img src="../img/blade_sym0.jpg" alt="" />bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. N&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, tr&#7915; Scatter <img src="../img/blade_sym12.jpg" alt="" />v&agrave; Split <img src="../img/blade_sym11.jpg" alt="" />, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t.</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n thanh to&aacute;n ri&ecirc;ng cho 2 hay nhi&#7873;u k&yacute; hi&#7879;u hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&#432; &#273;&atilde; th&#7845;y trong paytable. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843; thay v&igrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n n&#7871;u s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; hoang d&atilde; l&agrave; l&#7899;n h&#417;n so v&#7899;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n (b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7913;ng Wild).</p>\r\n<p><strong>nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline c&#7909; th&#7875;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter trong k&#7871;t qu&#7843; quay, c&aacute;c thanh to&aacute;n thu &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o payline th&#7855;ng. Vi&#7879;c thanh to&aacute;n cho nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, b&#7845;t k&#7875; v&#7883; tr&iacute;, 15 Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng v&#7899;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n n&#259;ng &#273;&#7897;ng (xem d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y). Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter c&#361;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; nh&#432; m&#7897;t hoang t&#7855;m v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; cho c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Split v&agrave; Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, t&#7915; "WILD EXTRA ''xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng khi ch&#417;i Free, ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao t&#7863;ng h&#417;n 15 tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chia</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Chia s&#7869; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n th&#7913; 5 sau khi m&#7897;t spin, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng trong b&#7845;t k&#7923; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia th&agrave;nh 2 v&agrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh l&agrave; 2 bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng gi&#7889;ng h&#7879;t nhau. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&#7853;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t qu&#7843; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7911;a 6 l&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875;.Chung ti&#7873;n cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7911;a 6 n&ecirc;u chi ti&#7871;t trong paytable.</p>\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Split l&agrave; c&oacute; s&#7861;n trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#7915; Scatter c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia khi thay th&#7871; nh&#432; t&#7855;m Wild.</p>\r\n<p><strong>C&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. &#272;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i ph&#7843;i b&#7845;m v&agrave;o <strong>Click to Start</strong> . M&#7897;t khi ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n, c&#7845;p cho ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n ban &#273;&#7847;u ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a X2, X3, X4 ho&#7863;c X5. M&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; b&#7845;t k&#7923; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; &#273;&oacute;. M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, sau &#273;&oacute; quay t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n<p>Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&#432;&#7907;c line, k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu v&agrave; s&#7889; d&ograve;ng l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng ch&#417;i.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; c&oacute; b&#432;&#7899;c nh&acirc;n c&#7911;a X2, X3, X4 v&agrave; X5. N&#7871;u ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i th&#7855;ng sau m&#7897;t spin, s&#7889; nh&acirc;n t&#259;ng l&ecirc;n m&#7897;t b&#432;&#7899;c (X5 l&agrave; cao nh&#7845;t) v&agrave; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; &#273;&oacute;. N&#7871;u kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau m&#7897;t spin, s&#7889; nh&acirc;n gi&#7843;m m&#7897;t b&#432;&#7899;c (X2 l&agrave; th&#7845;p nh&#7845;t). C&aacute;c d&ograve;ng kh&aacute;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i, c&#417; h&#7897;i l&#7899;n h&#417;n ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i c&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; gia t&#259;ng s&#7889; nh&acirc;n. Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter c&#361;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; nh&#432; m&#7897;t hoang t&#7855;m, thay th&#7871; t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#7915; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Split v&agrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild.</p>\r\n<p>V&agrave;o cu&#7889;i c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t chi ti&#7871;t c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng th&#7855;ng xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n. &#272;&#7875; tr&#7903; l&#7841;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c</strong> .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot l&agrave; m&#7897;t &#273;a c&#7845;p ti&#7871;n b&#7897; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i jackpot m&agrave; c&oacute; s&#7861;n trong t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&#7899;i t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel.M&#7897;t t&#7927; l&#7879; nh&#7887; c&#7911;a m&#7895;i c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel, b&#7903;i m&#7895;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y trong m&#7895;i nhi&#7873;u s&ograve;ng b&#7841;c tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o jackpot l&#361;y ti&#7871;n.</p>\r\n<p>Vi&#7879;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&agrave; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot l&agrave; ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; x&#7843;y ra sau khi b&#7845;t k&#7923; quay trong b&#7845;t k&#7923; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t. N&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; do b&#7845;t k&#7923; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&agrave; th&#7853;m ch&iacute; m&#7897;t spin m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;i&#7873;u g&igrave; trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; v&#7853;y, b&#7845;t k&#7923; c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot.Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c&#417; h&#7897;i k&iacu