(54, 'A', '<p><strong>5-Reel Slots 25-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a Bonus Bears l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ch&#7885;n k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>+</strong> v&agrave; <strong>&acirc; &euro; "</strong> n&uacute;t tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>Ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>Bet m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng</strong> n&uacute;t. M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c line. C&aacute;c con s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c n&uacute;t tr&ecirc;n c&#7843; hai b&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n cho bi&#7871;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n hi&#7879;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline. M&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#7871;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n t&#7889;i &#273;a, nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a s&#7869; thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p l&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu.</li>\r\n<li>Ch&#7885;n payline c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Ch&#7885;n d&ograve;ng</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t payline, ho&#7863;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c n&uacute;t m&agrave;u tr&ecirc;n c&#7843; hai m&#7863;t c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng. B&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t payline cao h&#417;n, b&#7841;n c&#361;ng s&#7869; ch&#7885;n t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p h&#417;n (v&iacute; d&#7909;, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline 18, payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 17 s&#7869; l&agrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; l&agrave; t&#7889;t). Nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet Max</strong> k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline v&#7899;i &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c t&#7889;i &#273;a cho m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng v&agrave; quay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>Reels c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng <strong>Auto Play</strong> ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. Chu&#7897;t tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c <strong>Auto Play</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y ch&#7885;n.Ch&#7885;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng ho&#7863;c ch&#7885;n <strong>Cho &#273;&#7871;n t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng</strong> quay cho &#273;&#7871;n khi c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7853;t ong ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o m&#7897;t t&ugrave;y ch&#7885;n kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng <strong>Auto Play</strong> ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. C&aacute;c <strong>Auto Play</strong> thay &#273;&#7893;i th&agrave;nh n&uacute;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> trong ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Play. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Play k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i, khi t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7853;t ong ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t n&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; ch&#7885;n <strong>cho &#273;&#7871;n t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng</strong> , ho&#7863;c khi b&#7841;n b&#7845;m <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>S&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i l&agrave; d&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>spin</strong> (n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7845;n <strong>Bet Max</strong> ) &#273;&#7875; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau khi h&#7885; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i (c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t payline b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o), b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng theo paytable. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>paytable</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; xem c&aacute;c paytable. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>quy</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; xem c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o<strong>game</strong> &#273;&#7875; quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u payline &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p<strong>Ch&#7885;n d&ograve;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i. Ti&#7873;n chung th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; gu&#7891;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>hoang d&atilde; Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild <img src="../img/bob_wild.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 2, 3 v&agrave; ch&#7881; c&#7843; 4 trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. N&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c h&#417;n <img src="../img/bob_scatter.jpg" alt="" />&#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t.</p>\r\n<p>3 <img src="../img/bob_wild.jpg" alt="" />&#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 2, 3 v&agrave; 4 trong khi ch&#417;i game k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t ch&iacute;nh c&#7911;a t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. N&#7871;u 3 <img src="../img/bob_wild.jpg" alt="" />k&yacute; t&#7921; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 2, 3 v&agrave; 4 trong t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; b&#7893; sung s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y <a href="#">&#7903; &#273;&acirc;y</a> .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Scatter Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter <img src="../img/bob_scatter.jpg" alt="" />kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n b&#7845;t k&#7923; payline c&#7909; th&#7875; v&agrave; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n c&#7843; trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y <a href="#">&#7903; &#273;&acirc;y</a> .</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u c&oacute; 2 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n <img src="../img/bob_scatter.jpg" alt="" />&#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7883; tr&iacute; n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n, c&aacute;c thanh to&aacute;n thu &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o payline th&#7855;ng.</p>\r\n<p>3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n <img src="../img/bob_scatter.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i &#7903; b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;&acirc;u trong gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7853;t ong nh&#432; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.</p>\r\n<p><strong>m&#7853;t ong Feature</strong></p>\r\n<p>B&#7845;m <strong>B&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u</strong> tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Honey.</p>\r\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh s&#7869; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t khu r&#7915;ng v&#7899;i 5 c&acirc;y c&oacute; th&#7875; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n cho g&#7845;u leo &#8203;&#8203;l&ecirc;n. Ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t c&acirc;y cho G&#7845;u &#273;&#7875; leo l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng n&agrave;y. Tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng l&ecirc;n c&acirc;y G&#7845;u s&#7869; ch&#7885;n ch&#7853;u m&#7853;t ong, m&#7895;i ti&#7871;t l&#7897; ho&#7863;c l&agrave; m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng ti&#7873;n m&#7863;t, ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t t&#7893; ong. Khi m&#7897;t t&#7893; ong &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ti&#7871;t l&#7897;, t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7853;t ong s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c. Trong t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7853;t ong b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 5 gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng ti&#7873;n m&#7863;t. M&#7895;i gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng ti&#7873;n m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a c&aacute;c v&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng M&#7853;t ong nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i 3, 4, 5, 7, 10, 15, 25, 50, 75, 100, ho&#7863;c 150.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ch&uacute; th&iacute;ch:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Khi m&#7897;t n&#7891;i m&#7853;t ong cho th&#7845;y m&#7897;t t&#7893; ong, b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7853;n gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng ti&#7873;n m&#7863;t trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n nh&acirc;n x2.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng M&#7853;t ong l&agrave; c&oacute; s&#7861;n c&#7843; trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>V&agrave;o cu&#7889;i nh&#7919;ng t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Honey, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh t&oacute;m t&#7855;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>&#272;&oacute;ng</strong> &#273;&#7875; quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p><a name="bob_freespinsfeat"></a><strong>quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>B&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o 3 <img src="../img/bob_wild.jpg" alt="" />&#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 2, 3 v&agrave; 4 trong ch&iacute;nh tr&ograve; ch&#417;i k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t 15 quay v&#7899;i m&#7897;t x3 th&#7855;ng nh&acirc;n.</p>\r\n<p>B&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o 3 <img src="../img/bob_wild.jpg" alt="" />&#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n 2, 3 v&agrave; 4 trong t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c retriggered, trao th&ecirc;m 15 quay mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. B&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; spin c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c retriggered v&ocirc;