(57, 'DB', '<p>Your objective is to predict the outcome of a bowling throw. First, place your bets by clicking the + and - buttons on the corresponding bet field. You can bet on the number of pins knocked down, on Strike (when all ten pins are downed with the first ball) or Spare (when all ten pins are downed with two balls). You can place several bets at once. When done placing your bets, click <strong>Throw </strong>. Two balls are now thrown (except in case of a strike, when the second ball is not thrown), and bets are settled. Click <strong>Throw </strong>again to place the same bets again. Clicking <strong>Clear Bets</strong>will remove all previously placed bets.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Golden Frame</strong></p>\r\n<p>Golden Frame is a special game round. If a strike is thrown during a Golden Frame, you win an amount that is 10x your total bet for this round. When a Golden Frame occurs, the frame result screen on the top right of the game area changes to a special image with the words "Golden Frame" on it.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong><br />The theoretical percentage return to player (RTP) in Bonus Bowling differs across bet types:<br /><br /></p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Bet Type</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>RTP</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Strike</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96.33%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Spare</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96.93%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>7 to 9</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96.53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>4 to 6</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96.53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>0 to 3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96.53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>', 'en'),
(58, 'DB', '<p>Tujuan Anda adalah untuk memprediksi hasil dari lemparan bowling. Pertama, menempatkan taruhan Anda dengan mengklik + dan - tombol di bidang taruhan yang sesuai. Anda dapat bertaruh pada jumlah pin knocked down, pada Mogok (ketika semua sepuluh pin jatuh dengan bola pertama) atau Spare (ketika semua sepuluh pin jatuh dengan dua bola). Anda dapat menempatkan beberapa taruhan sekaligus. Ketika dilakukan menempatkan taruhan Anda, klik <strong>Throw</strong> . Dua bola sekarang dilemparkan (kecuali dalam kasus pemogokan, ketika bola kedua tidak dilemparkan), dan taruhan diselesaikan. Klik <strong>Lempar</strong> lagi untuk menempatkan taruhan yang sama lagi. Mengklik <strong>Batal Taruhan</strong> akan menghapus semua taruhan sebelumnya ditempatkan.</p>\r\n<p><strong>emas Bingkai</strong></p>\r\n<p>Emas Frame adalah putaran permainan khusus. Jika mogok dilemparkan selama Frame Golden, Anda menang jumlah yang 10x total taruhan Anda untuk putaran ini. Ketika Frame Emas terjadi, layar hasil frame di kanan atas area permainan berubah menjadi gambar khusus dengan kata-kata "Golden Frame" di atasnya.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kembali ke Player</strong><br />The teoritis persentase kembali ke pemain (RTP) di Bonus Bowling berbeda antar jenis taruhan:<br /><br /></p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Jenis taruhan</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>RTP</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Menyerang</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,33%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Meluangkan</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,93%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>7-9</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>4 sampai 6</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>0-3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'id'),
(59, 'DB', '<p>M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a b&#7841;n l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; d&#7921; &#273;o&aacute;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; c&#7911;a m&#7897;t n&eacute;m bowling. &#272;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t + v&agrave; - tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c l&#297;nh v&#7921;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng ch&acirc;n g&otilde; xu&#7889;ng, tr&ecirc;n Strike (khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; m&#432;&#7901;i ch&acirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7855;n r&#417;i v&#7899;i b&oacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n) ho&#7863;c t&ugrave;ng (khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; m&#432;&#7901;i ch&acirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7855;n r&#417;i v&#7899;i hai qu&#7843; b&oacute;ng). B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t v&agrave;i c&#432;&#7907;c c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t l&uacute;c. Khi th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Throw</strong> . Hai qu&#7843; b&oacute;ng &#273;ang n&eacute;m (ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p cu&#7897;c &#273;&igrave;nh c&ocirc;ng, khi b&oacute;ng th&#7913; hai l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng n&eacute;m) v&agrave; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thanh to&aacute;n. Nh&#7845;n <strong>N&eacute;m</strong> m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a. Nh&#7845;p <strong>r&otilde; r&agrave;ng Bets</strong> s&#7869; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Khung v&agrave;ng</strong></p>\r\n<p>V&agrave;ng Frame l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t. N&#7871;u m&#7897;t cu&#7897;c t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&eacute;m trong m&#7897;t khung v&agrave;ng, b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n m&agrave; l&agrave; 10x t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n cho v&ograve;ng n&agrave;y. Khi m&#7897;t khung v&agrave;ng x&#7843;y ra, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh k&#7871;t qu&#7843; khung ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a khu v&#7921;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i thay &#273;&#7893;i sang m&#7897;t h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t v&#7899;i d&ograve;ng ch&#7919; "Khung v&agrave;ng" tr&ecirc;n &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong><br />T&#7927; l&#7879; tr&#7843; l&#7841;i l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i (RTP) trong Bonus Bowling kh&aacute;c nhau gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#432;&#7907;c:<br /><br /></p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Lo&#7841;i c&#432;&#7907;c</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>RTP</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&#272;&igrave;nh c&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,33%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>thay th&#7871;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,93%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>7-9</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>4-6</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>0-3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>96,53%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>', 'vn'),
