(62, '7', '<p><strong>3-Reel 5-Line Slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>The object of Bermuda Triangle is to obtain a winning symbol combination on a payline by spinning the reels.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong> There is a difference between the line bet and the total bet. The line bet shows how much you''re betting on a single payline. The total bet shows how much you''re spending in this game round.&Acirc;&nbsp;The payouts shown in the paytable are multiplied by the coin size, not the line bet. If you get winning combinations on more than one payline, the winnings for each payline are added up.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To play the game:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Choose the value of the coins you wish to wager each round, by clicking on the + and &ndash; buttons on the left of the screen.</li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Bet One</strong> or <strong>Bet Max</strong> to select the number of coins you wish to wager. Each click on the <strong>Bet One</strong> button adds another coin to the bet. One payline is activated for every coin you bet. You will only win if a combination occurs on an activated payline. You will only win if a combination occurs on an activated payline. Clicking <strong>Bet Max</strong> increases the number of paylines to the maximum &ndash; that is, five paylines &ndash; and spins the reels automatically.</li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Spin</strong> (if you did not press Bet Max), or click on the arm, to spin the reels.</li>\r\n<li>If the reels show a winning combination after they stop (along an activated payline), you win according to the winning table (see the top panel of the machine). To find the winning amount, multiply your coin value with the number in the winnings table (on the appropriate row). If you win on multiple lines simultaneously, your winnings are added up.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>The theoretical percentage return to player (RTP) is 96.73%.</p>', 'en'),
(63, '7', '<p><strong>3-Reel 5-Line Slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>Objek Segitiga Bermuda adalah untuk mendapatkan kombinasi simbol menang pada payline dengan memutar reel.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Harap dicatat:</strong> Ada perbedaan antara garis taruhan dan total taruhan. Taruhan garis menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda bertaruh pada payline tunggal. Total taruhan menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda menghabiskan dalam game ini round.&Acirc; The pembayaran ditampilkan dalam paytable dikalikan dengan ukuran koin, bukan garis taruhan. Jika Anda mendapatkan kombinasi pemenang pada lebih dari satu payline, kemenangan untuk setiap payline yang ditambahkan.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Untuk memainkan permainan:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pilih nilai dari uang yang Anda ingin bertaruh setiap putaran, dengan mengklik + dan - tombol di sebelah kiri layar.</li>\r\n<li>Klik <strong>Bet Satu</strong> atau <strong>Bet Max</strong> untuk memilih jumlah uang yang Anda ingin bertaruh. Setiap klik pada <strong>Bet Satu</strong> tombol menambahkan koin lain untuk taruhan. Salah satu payline diaktifkan untuk setiap koin Anda bertaruh. Anda hanya akan menang jika kombinasi terjadi pada payline aktif. Anda hanya akan menang jika kombinasi terjadi pada payline aktif. Mengklik <strong>Bet Max</strong> meningkatkan jumlah paylines secara maksimal - yaitu, lima paylines - dan berputar gulungan otomatis.</li>\r\n<li>Klik <strong>Putar</strong> (jika Anda tidak menekan Bet Max), atau klik pada lengan, untuk memutar gulungan.</li>\r\n<li>Jika gulungan menunjukkan kombinasi yang unggul setelah mereka berhenti (sepanjang payline diaktifkan), Anda menang berdasarkan tabel menang (lihat panel atas mesin). Untuk menemukan jumlah menang, kalikan nilai koin Anda dengan nomor pada tabel kemenangan (pada baris yang sesuai). Jika Anda menang pada beberapa baris secara bersamaan, kemenangan Anda yang ditambahkan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Kembali ke Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>Teoritis persentase kembali ke pemain (RTP) adalah 96,73%.</p>', 'id'),
(64, '7', '<p><strong>3-Reel 5 &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y Slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Tam gi&aacute;c Bermuda l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang chi ti&ecirc;u trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y round.&Acirc; C&aacute;c ti&ecirc;n chi th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu, kh&ocirc;ng c&#432;&#7907;c line. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ch&#7885;n gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i v&ograve;ng, b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t + v&agrave; - tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>Bet M&#7897;t</strong> ho&#7863;c <strong>Bet Max</strong> &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c. M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Bet M&#7897;t</strong> n&uacute;t th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c.