(67, '14', '<p><strong>3-Reel Standard Slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>The object of Crazy 7 is to obtain a winning symbol combination by spinning the reels.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong> There is a difference between the line bet and the total bet. The line bet shows how much you''re betting on a single payline. The total bet shows how much you''re spending in this game round.&Acirc;&nbsp;The payouts shown in the paytable are multiplied by the coin size, not the line bet. If you get winning combinations on more than one payline, the winnings for each payline are added up.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To play the game:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Choose the value of the coins you wish to wager each round, by clicking on the + and &ndash; buttons on the left of the screen.</li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Bet One</strong> or <strong>Bet Max</strong> to select the number of coins you wish to wager. Each click on the <strong>Bet One</strong> button adds another coin to the bet.</li>\r\n<li>You can also bet by clicking on the corresponding column in the paytable (the leftmost column bets one coin, the middle column bets two and the rightmost column bets three coins). The reels will start to spin automatically.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Bet Max</strong> increases the number of paylines to the maximum &acirc;&euro;&ldquo; that is, three lines &acirc;&euro;&ldquo; and spins the reels automatically.</li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Spin</strong> (if you did not press Bet Max or use the paytable), or click on the arm, to spin the reels.</li>\r\n<li>If the reels show a winning combination after they stop (along the payline), you win according to the paytable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>The theoretical percentage return to player (RTP) is 97.21%.</p>', 'en'),
(68, '14', '<p><strong>3-Reel Standard Slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>Objek Crazy 7 adalah untuk mendapatkan kombinasi simbol menang dengan memutar reel.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Harap dicatat:</strong> Ada perbedaan antara garis taruhan dan total taruhan. Taruhan garis menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda bertaruh pada payline tunggal. Total taruhan menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda menghabiskan dalam game ini round.&Acirc; The pembayaran ditampilkan dalam paytable dikalikan dengan ukuran koin, bukan garis taruhan. Jika Anda mendapatkan kombinasi pemenang pada lebih dari satu payline, kemenangan untuk setiap payline yang ditambahkan.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Untuk memainkan permainan:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pilih nilai dari uang yang Anda ingin bertaruh setiap putaran, dengan mengklik + dan - tombol di sebelah kiri layar.</li>\r\n<li>Klik <strong>Bet Satu</strong> atau <strong>Bet Max</strong> untuk memilih jumlah uang yang Anda ingin bertaruh. Setiap klik pada <strong>Bet Satu</strong> tombol menambahkan koin lain untuk taruhan.</li>\r\n<li>Anda juga bisa bertaruh dengan mengklik pada kolom yang sesuai dalam paytable (paling kiri taruhan kolom satu koin, kolom taruhan tengah dua kolom taruhan paling kanan tiga koin). Gulungan akan mulai berputar secara otomatis.</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Bet Max</strong> meningkatkan jumlah paylines secara maksimal &acirc; &euro; "yaitu, tiga baris &acirc; &euro;" dan berputar gulungan otomatis.</li>\r\n<li>Klik <strong>Putar</strong> (jika Anda tidak menekan Bet Max atau menggunakan paytable), atau klik pada lengan, untuk memutar gulungan.</li>\r\n<li>Jika gulungan menunjukkan kombinasi yang unggul setelah mereka berhenti (sepanjang payline), Anda menang berdasarkan paytable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Kembali ke Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>Teoritis persentase kembali ke pemain (RTP) adalah 97,21%.</p>', 'id'),
(69, '14', '<p><strong>3-Reel Slots chu&#7849;n</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Crazy 7 l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang chi ti&ecirc;u trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y round.&Acirc; C&aacute;c ti&ecirc;n chi th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu, kh&ocirc;ng c&#432;&#7907;c line. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ch&#7885;n gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i v&ograve;ng, b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t + v&agrave; - tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>Bet M&#7897;t</strong> ho&#7863;c <strong>Bet Max</strong> &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n c&#432;&#7907;c. M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Bet M&#7897;t</strong> n&uacute;t th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c.</li>\r\n<li>B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o c&aacute;c c&#7897;t t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng trong paytable (t&#7853;n c&ugrave;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7897;t m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7897;t gi&#7919;a hai v&agrave; c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7897;t ngo&agrave;i c&ugrave;ng b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i ba &#273;&#7891;ng ti&#7873;n). C&aacute;c cu&#7897;n s&#7869; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u quay t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet Max</strong> t&#259;ng s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng payline &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c t&#7889;i &#273;a &acirc; &euro; "c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave;, ba d&ograve;ng &acirc; &euro;" v&agrave; quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>spin</strong> (n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7845;n Bet Max ho&#7863;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng paytable), ho&#7863;c click v&agrave;o c&aacute;nh tay, &#273;&#7875; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau khi h&#7885; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i (c&ugrave;ng payline), b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng theo paytable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; c&#7847;u th&#7911;</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&#7927; l&#7879; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i (RTP) l&agrave; 97,21%.</p>', 'vn'),
