#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c thanh to&aacute;n trong game.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>l&#7841;i</strong> tho&aacute;t ra kh&#7887;i <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p + ho&#7863;c - d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i. Ti&#7873;n chung th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n l&#7841;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>hoang d&atilde; Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>Captain America - The First Avenger c&oacute; 2 bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng hoang d&atilde;: <img src="../img/cam_wild_good.jpg" alt="" />v&agrave; <img src="../img/cam_wild_bad.jpg" alt="" />. C&#7843; hai &#273;&#7873;u c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; <img src="../img/cam_scatter.jpg" alt="" />v&agrave; <img src="../img/cam_freegames.jpg" alt="" />, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t.</p>\r\n<p>B&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o <img src="../img/cam_wild_good.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n reel # 1 k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i <img src="../img/cam_freegames.jpg" alt="" />b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n reel # 3, v&agrave; <img src="../img/cam_wild_bad.jpg" alt="" />b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n reel # 5 trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, c&aacute;c si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y <a href="#">&#7903; &#273;&acirc;y</a> .</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n thanh to&aacute;n ri&ecirc;ng cho 2 hay nhi&#7873;u k&yacute; hi&#7879;u hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&#432; &#273;&atilde; th&#7845;y trong paytable. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843; thay v&igrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n n&#7871;u s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; hoang d&atilde; l&agrave; l&#7899;n h&#417;n so v&#7899;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n (b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7913;ng Wild).</p>\r\n<p><strong>L&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> <img src="../img/cam_wild_good.jpg" alt="" /> &#273;&ocirc;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng khi tham gia m&#7897;t s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng v&#7899;i <img src="../img/cam_bucky.jpg" alt="" />, <img src="../img/cam_shield.jpg" alt="" />ho&#7863;c <img src="../img/cam_chain.jpg" alt="" />trong c&#7843; hai tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng.</p>\r\n<p><img src="../img/cam_wild_bad.jpg" alt="" />&#273;&ocirc;i th&#7855;ng khi tham gia m&#7897;t s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng v&#7899;i <img src="../img/cam_cross.jpg" alt="" />, <img src="../img/cam_nazi.jpg" alt="" />ho&#7863;c <img src="../img/cam_hydra.jpg" alt="" />trong c&#7843; hai tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh v&agrave; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Scatter Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter <img src="../img/cam_scatter.jpg" alt="" />kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; payline c&#7909; th&#7875;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; 2 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng sau khi m&#7897;t tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; quay, c&aacute;c thanh to&aacute;n thu &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o payline th&#7855;ng, n&#7871;u c&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src="../img/cam_freegames.jpg" alt="" />l&agrave; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t trong Captain America - The First Avenger game. N&oacute; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n reel # 3 trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh ch&#7881; &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ra m&#7897;t s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i <img src="../img/cam_wild_good.jpg" alt="" />v&agrave; <img src="../img/cam_wild_bad.jpg" alt="" />, do &#273;&oacute; g&acirc;y ra c&aacute;c si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p><a name="superenergyFG"></a><strong>Si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o <img src="../img/cam_wild_good.jpg" alt="" />, <img src="../img/cam_freegames.jpg" alt="" />v&agrave; <img src="../img/cam_wild_bad.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh &#7903; b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n reel # 1, # 3 v&agrave; # 5 t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng.</p>\r\n<p>&#272;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&ograve;ng b&#7845;m v&agrave;o <strong>Click to Start</strong> . B&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng trao 4 ban &#273;&#7847;u tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. Nh&#7845;n <strong>Continue</strong>&#273;&#7875; chuy&#7875;n sang m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ti&#7871;p theo.</p>\r\n<p>M&#7897;t m&#7841;ng l&#432;&#7899;i c&aacute;c &ocirc; vu&ocirc;ng 3x3 xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n. M&#7895;i ph&ograve;ng trong s&#7889; 9 h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho m&#7897;t t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;i&#7879;n nh&#432; m&ocirc; t&#7843; d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr><th><strong>Symbol On The L&#432;&#7899;i</strong></th><th><strong>t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng &#273;i&#7879;n</strong></th></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center><img src="../img/cam_4fg.jpg" alt="" /></center></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>4 th&ecirc;m si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i. 3 c&#7911;a c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t tr&ecirc;n l&#432;&#7899;i &#273;i&#7879;n ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y l&agrave;m cho n&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; cho b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 12 tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; b&#7893; sung trong m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng duy nh&#7845;t.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center><img src="../img/cam_x1.jpg" alt="" /></center></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c nh&acirc;n hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i c&#7911;a si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#259;ng x1. 3 c&#7911;a c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t tr&ecirc;n l&#432;&#7899;i &#273;i&#7879;n ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y l&agrave;m cho n&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; cho b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n x3 th&ecirc;m x1 t&#7841;i m&#7897;t th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center><img src="../img/cam_fgretrigger.jpg" alt="" /></center></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img src="../img/cam_stone.jpg" alt="" />&#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; reel # 3 ch&#7881; trong si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. B&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o n&oacute; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n &#273;&oacute; reel trong c&aacute;c k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin, 4 Super Energy ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center><img src="../img/cam_wild_good.jpg" alt="" />ho&#7863;c l&agrave;<img src="../img/cam_wild_bad.jpg" alt="" /></center></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng cho th&#7845;y ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng Wilds trong si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p theo: b&#7845;t c&#7913; khi n&agrave;o n&oacute; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t cu&#7897;n v&agrave; t&#7841;o ra m&#7897;t s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng n&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7903; r&#7897;ng, bao g&#7891;m to&agrave;n b&#7897; reel &#273;&#7875; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh m&#7903; r&#7897;ng Wild. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c v&#7883; tr&iacute; tr&ecirc;n reel n&agrave;y tr&#7903; n&ecirc;n hoang d&atilde; v&agrave; t&#7845;t c&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><center><img src="../img/cam_superspin.jpg" alt="" /></center></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>2 Super spin - Spin Villain Super v&agrave; c&aacute;c anh h&ugrave;ng si&ecirc;u Spin - &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao sau khi c&aacute;c si&ecirc;u n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&atilde; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>The Hero si&ecirc;u spin t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng <img src="../img/cam_wild_good.jpg" alt="" />nh&#432; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng Wild reel # 1 v&agrave; nh&#432; m&#7897;t hoang t&#7855;m th&ecirc;m ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7883; tr&iacute; c&#7911;a 4 cu&#7897;n c&ograve;n l&#7841;i. Ch&#7881; c&oacute; A, K, Q, J, 10, 9, <img src="../img/cam_bucky.jpg" alt="" />, <img src="../img/cam_shield.jpg" alt="" />, <img src="../img/cam_chain.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n trong c&aacute;c anh h&ugrave;ng si&ecirc;u spin.</p>\r\n<p>The Villain Si&ecirc;u spin t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng <img src="../img/cam_wild_bad.jpg" alt="" />nh&#432; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng Wild reel # 5 v&agrave; nh&#432; m&#7897;t hoang t&#7855;m th&ecirc;m ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7883; tr&iacute; c&#7911;a 4 cu&#7897;n c&ograve;n l&#7841;i. Ch&#7881; c&oacute; A, K, Q, J, 10, 9, <img src="../img/cam_cross.jpg" alt="" />, <img src="../img/cam_nazi.jpg" alt="" />, <img src="../img/cam_hydra.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n trong Villain Si&ecirc;u spin.</p>\r\n<p><strong>L&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> t&#7855;m hoang bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&oacute;