(82, '11', '<p><strong>5-Reel Slots with a Progressive Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>The object of Cinerama is to obtain a winning symbol combination by spinning the reels. The better your symbol combination, the bigger the payout.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To play the game:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Select the number of paylines you want to activate (in other words, to bet on) by clicking on the <strong>Bet One</strong> button or the payline number left or right of the reels. When you click on payline number 3 for example, you also activate paylines 1 and 2. Each click on the <strong>Bet One</strong> buttons activates one more payline. Click <strong>Bet Max</strong> or payline number 5 to select all paylines. Remember that your total bet (the amount you spend on the game round) is line bet x number of lines selected. Clicking <strong>Bet Max</strong> will also spin the reels automatically.</li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Spin</strong> (if you did not press <strong>Bet Max</strong>) to spin the reels.</li>\r\n<li>If the reels show a winning combination after they stop (along an activated payline), you win according to the winning table. Click the<strong>Paytable</strong>button to see the paytable, if you wish. Close the paytable by clicking the Paytable button again. If you win on multiple paylines simultaneously, your winnings are added up.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Active paylines are represented by lines that appear over the reels. You can activate paylines and see their shape by progressively clicking the<strong>Bet One </strong>button.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong> You only win if a combination occurs on an active payline. The Scatter symbol is an exception to these rules. More information about the Scatter symbol can be found below.</p>\r\n<p>The Bonus Round 1 symbol is an exception to that rule. Read more about Bonus Round symbols below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About the Paytable:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The tables show a win multiplier for every hit amount for every symbol. For example, if you have four Spotlight symbols in a row on an activated payline, starting on the leftmost reel, you have four hits. Read the number on the line &ldquo;4x&rdquo; next to that symbol. Multiply that symbol by your line bet to get your win amount. If you have winning combinations on more than one line, add them all up to get the total win amount. The symbols have to lie consecutively, starting from the leftmost reel, to qualify as hits.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong> There is a difference between the line bet and the total bet. The line bet shows how much you''re betting on a single payline. The total bet shows how much you''re spending in this game round. The payouts shown in the paytable are multiplied by the line bet, not by the total bet. If you get winning combinations on more than one payline, the winnings for each payline are added up.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bonus Rounds:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Director and Headphone symbols are bonus symbols. These symbols do not grant you any winnings, but they enable you to enter the Bonus Round. There is two bonus rounds in Cinerama. For Bonus Round 1, you need to get the Headphone symbol anywhere on the first reel. It does not matter if it is on an activated payline or not.</p>\r\n<p>For Bonus Round 2, you need to get three consecutive Director symbols on an activated payline, starting from the leftmost reel.</p>\r\n<p>When you enter a bonus round, follow the instructions on the screen. You will be paid a prize according to the choice(s) you make.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Progressive Jackpot, Scatter and Wild symbols</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>One of the possible wins in this game is the progressive Jackpot, built up by all the casinos that offer the game. A small percentage of each bet, by every person playing this game in each of many online casinos, is added to a common pot. When a player gets the right result, that player wins the entire Jackpot (in some games you can also win part of it).</p>\r\n<p>After a Jackpot has been won, a new pot is started, with the casinos contributing a base amount of money (called a seed). This ensures that even if you get a Jackpot result in a game right after someone else has won the Jackpot, you will still get a large win.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>In some games you have to make a specific bet to be eligible for the Jackpot.</li>\r\n<li>If you get disconnected in the middle of a game round, your game does not change the value of the Jackpot. The state of the game up to that point is remembered by the casino; the next time you log in you can finish your game round with the same odds and without placing a new bet.</li>\r\n<li>If a Jackpot is being discontinued (a game is closed and removed from the casino client), you will be notified of it by the casino.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Jackpot for this game works like this:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Seed (how much money the Jackpot starts out with):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>300&nbsp;000 x coin size</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Contribution rate (what percentage of each bet goes into the Jackpot):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>1%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Win condition (the result you have to get to win the Jackpot):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Five wild symbols on an active payline.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Win requirements (what you need to do to be eligible for the Jackpot):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Play for max bet.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>The Camera symbol is also a wild symbol &ndash; meaning it stands for any other symbol, except the Director and Headphone symbols, and forms winning combinations in a way most profitable for the player.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>The theoretical percentage return to player (RTP) is 96.94%.</p>', 'en'),
(83, '11', '<p><strong>Slot 5-Reel dengan Progressive Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>Objek Cinerama adalah untuk mendapatkan kombinasi simbol menang dengan memutar reel. Semakin baik kombinasi simbol Anda, semakin besar payout.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Untuk memainkan permainan:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pilih jumlah paylines Anda ingin mengaktifkan (dengan kata lain, untuk bertaruh pada) dengan mengklik <strong>Bet Satu</strong> tombol atau jumlah payline kiri atau kanan gulungan. Ketika Anda mengklik pada payline nomor 3 misalnya, Anda juga mengaktifkan paylines 1 dan 2. Setiap klik pada<strong>Bet Satu</strong> tombol mengaktifkan satu payline lagi. Klik <strong>Bet Max</strong> atau payline nomor 5 untuk memilih semua paylines. Ingat bahwa total taruhan Anda (jumlah yang Anda belanjakan pada putaran permainan) adalah taruhan garis x jumlah baris yang dipilih. Mengklik <strong>Bet Max</strong> juga akan memutar gulungan secara otomatis.</li>\r\n<li>Klik <strong>Putar</strong> (jika Anda tidak menekan <strong>Bet Max</strong> ) untuk memutar gulungan.</li>\r\n<li>Jika gulungan menunjukkan kombinasi yang unggul setelah mereka berhenti (sepanjang payline diaktifkan), Anda menang berdasarkan tabel menang. Klik <strong>Paytable</strong> tombol untuk melihat paytable, jika Anda inginkan. Tutup paytable dengan mengklik tombol Paytable lagi. Jika Anda menang pada beberapa paylines secara bersamaan, kemenangan Anda yang ditambahkan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Paylines aktif diwakili oleh garis-garis yang muncul di atas gulungan. Anda dapat mengaktifkan paylines dan melihat bentuk mereka dengan semakin mengklik <strong>Bet Satu</strong> tombol.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Harap dicatat:</strong> Anda hanya menang jika kombinasi terjadi pada payline aktif. Simbol Scatter merupakan pengecualian aturan ini. Informasi lebih lanjut tentang simbol Scatter dapat ditemukan di bawah.</p>\r\n<p>Bonus Putaran 1 simbol merupakan pengecualian untuk aturan itu. Baca lebih lanjut tentang Putaran simbol Bonus bawah.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tentang Paytable tersebut:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tabel menunjukkan multiplier menang untuk setiap jumlah hit untuk setiap simbol. Misalnya, jika Anda memiliki empat simbol Spotlight berturut-turut pada payline aktif, mulai dari gulungan paling kiri, Anda memiliki empat hits. Membaca nomor pada baris "4x" di samping simbol itu. Kalikan simbol bahwa dengan taruhan baris Anda untuk mendapatkan jumlah menang Anda. Jika Anda telah memenangkan kombinasi dari lebih dari satu baris, tambahkan mereka semua untuk mendapatkan jumlah total menang. Simbol harus berbohong berturut-turut, mulai dari gulungan paling kiri, untuk memenuhi syarat sebagai hits.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Harap dicatat:</strong> Ada perbedaan antara garis taruhan dan total taruhan. Taruhan garis menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda bertaruh pada payline tunggal. Total taruhan menunjukkan berapa banyak Anda menghabiskan di babak permainan ini. Pembayaran ditampilkan dalam paytable dikalikan dengan taruhan baris, bukan oleh total taruhan. Jika Anda mendapatkan kombinasi pemenang pada lebih dari satu payline, kemenangan untuk setiap payline yang ditambahkan.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bonus Rounds:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Direktur dan Headphone simbol adalah simbol bonus. Simbol-simbol ini tidak memberikan Anda kemenangan, tapi mereka memungkinkan Anda untuk memasukkan Bonus Putaran. Ada dua putaran bonus di Cinerama. Untuk Bonus Putaran 1, Anda perlu untuk mendapatkan simbol Headphone di mana saja di reel pertama. Tidak peduli apakah itu pada payline aktif atau tidak.</p>\r\n<p>Untuk Bonus Putaran 2, Anda perlu untuk mendapatkan tiga simbol Direktur berturut-turut pada payline aktif, mulai dari gulungan paling kiri.</p>\r\n<p>Bila Anda memasukkan putaran bonus, ikuti petunjuk di layar. Anda akan dibayar hadiah sesuai dengan pilihan (s) yang Anda buat.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Progressive Jackpot, Menyebarkan dan simbol Liar</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>hadiah main kartu</strong></p>\r\n<p>Salah satu kemenangan mungkin dalam permainan ini adalah progresif Jackpot, dibangun oleh semua kasino yang menawarkan permainan.Sebagian kecil masing-masing taruhan, oleh setiap orang memainkan game ini di masing-masing banyak kasino online, ditambahkan ke pot umum.Ketika seorang pemain mendapat hasil yang tepat, pemain yang memenangkan seluruh Jackpot (dalam beberapa permainan Anda juga bisa menang bagian dari itu).</p>\r\n<p>Setelah Jackpot telah dimenangkan, pot baru dimulai, dengan kontribusi sejumlah kasino dasar uang (disebut benih). Hal ini memastikan bahwa bahkan jika Anda mendapatkan hasil Jackpot dalam permainan segera setelah seseorang telah memenangkan Jackpot, Anda masih akan mendapatkan kemenangan yang besar.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tolong dicatat:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dalam beberapa permainan Anda harus membuat taruhan yang spesifik untuk memenuhi persyaratan untuk Jackpot.</li>\r\n<li>Jika Anda terputus di tengah putaran permainan, permainan Anda tidak mengubah nilai Jackpot. Keadaan permainan sampai titik yang diingat oleh kasino; pada saat Anda login Anda dapat menyelesaikan putaran permainan Anda dengan peluang yang sama dan tanpa menempatkan taruhan baru.</li>\r\n<li>Jika Jackpot sedang dihentikan (permainan ditutup dan dihapus dari klien kasino), Anda akan diberitahu dengan kasino.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Jackpot untuk permainan ini bekerja seperti ini:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Benih (berapa banyak uang Jackpot dimulai dengan):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>300 000 x ukuran koin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Tingkat kontribusi (persentase masing-masing taruhan masuk ke Jackpot):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>1%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Kondisi Win (hasil Anda harus mendapatkan untuk memenangkan Jackpot):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Lima simbol liar pada payline aktif.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>persyaratan Win (apa yang harus Anda lakukan untuk memenuhi persyaratan untuk Jackpot):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Bermain untuk max bet.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Simbol Kamera juga merupakan simbol liar - yang berarti singkatan untuk setiap simbol lain, kecuali Direktur dan Headphone simbol, dan bentuk-bentuk kombinasi pemenang dengan cara yang paling menguntungkan untuk pemain.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kembali ke Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>Teoritis persentase kembali ke pemain (RTP) adalah 96,94%.</p>', 'id'),
(84, '11', '<p><strong>Slots 5-Reel v&#7899;i Progressive Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Cinerama l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7911;a b&#7841;n t&#7889;t h&#417;n, l&#7899;n h&#417;n c&aacute;c thanh to&aacute;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ch&#7885;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng payline b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t (n&oacute;i c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c, &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o) b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Bet M&#7897;t</strong> n&uacute;t ho&#7863;c s&#7889; payline tr&aacute;i ho&#7863;c b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n. Khi b&#7841;n nh&#7845;n chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o payline s&#7889; 3 v&iacute; d&#7909;, b&#7841;n c&#361;ng k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline 1 v&agrave; 2. M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Bet M&#7897;t</strong> n&uacute;t k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&#7897;t payline h&#417;n. Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>Bet Max</strong> ho&#7863;c payline s&#7889; 5 &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline. H&atilde;y nh&#7899; r&#7857;ng t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n (s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n chi ti&ecirc;u v&agrave;o c&aacute;c v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i) l&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c line x s&#7889; d&ograve;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet Max</strong> c&#361;ng s&#7869; xoay gu&#7891;ng t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>spin</strong> (n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7845;n <strong>Bet Max</strong> ) &#273;&#7875; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau khi h&#7885; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i (c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t payline k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t), b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng theo b&#7843;ng th&#7855;ng. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o<strong>paytable</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; xem paytable, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n. &#272;&oacute;ng paytable b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t paytable m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u payline &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline v&agrave; xem h&igrave;nh d&#7841;ng c&#7911;a h&#7885; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Bet M&#7897;t</strong> n&uacute;t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> B&#7841;n ch&#7881; c&oacute; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng n&#7871;u k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c.Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p>Bonus Round 1 bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; cho quy t&#7855;c &#273;&oacute;. T&igrave;m hi&#7875;u th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng v&ograve;ng Bonus d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; paytable:</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c b&#7843;ng hi&#7875;n th&#7883; m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cho m&#7895;i s&#7889; ti&#7873;n hit cho m&#7895;i bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. V&iacute; d&#7909;, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n c&oacute; b&#7889;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Spotlight trong m&#7897;t h&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&agrave;o gu&#7891;ng t&#7853;n c&ugrave;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, b&#7841;n c&oacute; b&#7889;n l&#432;&#7907;t truy c&#7853;p. &#272;&#7885;c s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n d&ograve;ng "4x" b&ecirc;n c&#7841;nh bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&oacute;. Nh&acirc;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&oacute; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, th&ecirc;m t&#7845;t c&#7843; ch&uacute;ng l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng. C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7843;i n&#7857;m li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p, b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; gu&#7891;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n nh&#432; truy c&#7853;p.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang chi ti&ecirc;u trong v&ograve;ng &#273;&#7845;u n&agrave;y. To&aacute;n t&#7927; l&#7879; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line, kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7857;ng t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng