g ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p h&#417;n (v&iacute; d&#7909;, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline 18, payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 17 s&#7869; l&agrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; l&agrave; t&#7889;t). B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet Max</strong> &#273;&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c payline v&agrave; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>S&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i l&agrave; d&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>spin</strong> (n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7845;n <strong>Bet Max</strong> ) &#273;&#7875; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng sau khi h&#7885; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i (c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t payline b&#7841;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o), b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng theo b&#7843;ng th&#7855;ng.Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>paytable</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; xem paytable, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n. &#272;&oacute;ng paytable b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>l&#7841;i</strong> n&uacute;t. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u payline &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline v&agrave; xem h&igrave;nh d&#7841;ng c&#7911;a h&#7885; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Ch&#7885;n d&ograve;ng</strong> n&uacute;t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> B&#7841;n ch&#7881; c&oacute; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng n&#7871;u k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c.Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang chi ti&ecirc;u trong v&ograve;ng &#273;&#7845;u n&agrave;y. To&aacute;n t&#7927; l&#7879; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line, kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7857;ng t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n paytable. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, nh&acirc;n d&ograve;ng c&aacute; l&agrave; do thanh to&aacute;n.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u hai k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p>S&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra t&#7915; tr&aacute;i sang ph&#7843;i, n&#7871;u kh&ocirc;ng n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thanh to&aacute;n.</p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; kh&aacute;c (tr&#7915; Scatter v&agrave; Bonus), &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n thanh to&aacute;n ri&ecirc;ng cho c&aacute;c k&yacute; hi&#7879;u hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng n&#7871;u nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n li&#7873;n k&#7873;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline c&#7909; th&#7875; - n&#7871;u c&oacute; hai ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u trong s&#7889; h&#7885; tr&ecirc;n l&#297;nh v&#7921;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i, b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng kh&aacute;c. Vi&#7879;c thanh to&aacute;n cho c&aacute;c k&yacute; hi&#7879;u ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng s&#7889; c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng bonus</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u th&#432;&#7903;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n nh&#7919;ng &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7847;u v&agrave; cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng, b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 20 spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t spin mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dollar b&oacute;ng</strong></p>\r\n<p>&#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t lotto lo&#7841;i sidegame ti&#7871;n b&#7897; n&#417;i b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n 5 con s&#7889; ra kh&#7887;i 49. Sau &#273;&oacute;, m&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, n&#259;m con s&#7889; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c r&uacute;t ra m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n. C&aacute;c con s&#7889; h&#417;n ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, b&#7841;n c&agrave;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. N&#7871;u t&#7845;t c&#7843; n&#259;m con s&#7889; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p, b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>Dollar b&oacute;ng n&#7857;m &#7903; ph&#7847;n tr&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. B&#7845;m v&agrave;o <strong>Enable</strong> &#273;&#7875; ch&#417;i n&oacute;. B&#7841;n s&#7869; th&#7845;y m&#7897;t t&#7853;p h&#7907;p c&aacute;c s&#7889; t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 49. Click v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#259;m ng&#432;&#7901;i h&#7885; ch&#7885;n th&#7911; c&ocirc;ng (click l&#7847;n n&#7919;a &#273;&#7875; b&#7887; ch&#7885;n), ho&#7863;c nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o <strong>l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n</strong> &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; n&oacute; l&agrave;m cho b&#7841;n t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n thay &#273;&#7893;i s&#7889; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n, nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o b&#7845;t k&#7923; c&#7911;a c&aacute;c con s&#7889; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n ch&uacute;ng, v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i m&#7899;i. Nh&#7845;n<strong>Activate</strong> &#273;&#7875; &#7849;n c&aacute;c con s&#7889; v&agrave; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Trong khi b&oacute;ng Dollar &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, m&#7897;t &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot b&#7893; sung &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng m&#7895;i khi b&#7841;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n m&#7897;t &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh. Gi&aacute; tr&#7883; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot l&agrave; c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; t&igrave;m th&#7845;y n&oacute; trong giao di&#7879;n Dollar Ball. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n h&#7911;y b&#7887; Ball tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Dollar, nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Disable</strong> .</p>\r\n<p>Dollar Ball s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i m&#7885;i tr&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;u ch&iacute;nh tr&ograve;n, v&#7899;i c&aacute;c con s&#7889; t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921;, cho &#273;&#7871;n khi b&#7841;n c&oacute; thay &#273;&#7893;i s&#7889; ho&#7863;c v&ocirc; hi&#7879;u h&oacute;a c&aacute;c sidegame.</p>\r\n<p>con s&#7889; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong m&#7897;t h&agrave;ng v&ograve;ng tr&ograve;n m&agrave;u tr&#7855;ng &#7903; ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. M&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&#7919;ng con s&#7889; r&uacute;t s&#7869; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n ngay ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n h&#7885;. N&#7871;u b&#7845;t k&#7923; c&#7911;a c&aacute;c con s&#7889; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, c&aacute;c v&ograve;ng tr&ograve;n c&oacute; ch&#7913;a nh&#7919;ng con s&#7889; n&agrave;y s&#7869; thay &#273;&#7893;i m&agrave;u s&#7855;c cho m&agrave;u xanh l&aacute; c&acirc;y v&agrave; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i. N&oacute; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o s&#7889; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i th&#7855;ng t&#7915; v&ograve;ng &#273;&#7845;u ch&iacute;nh. th&#7855;ng Dollar b&oacute;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7843; theo paytable cho Dollar b&oacute;ng m&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y trong c&aacute;c paytable tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh. Th&#7855;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7915; 1, 2, ho&#7863;c 3 con s&#7889; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng v&agrave; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&acirc;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot b&#7903;i s&#7889; nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh.</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i nh&#7919;ng th&#7855;ng c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh, Dollar b&oacute;ng bao g&#7891;m chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ti&#7871;n b&#7897;. M&#7897;t t&#7927; l&#7879; nh&#7887; c&#7911;a m&#7895;i c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o n&#7891;i chung c&#7911;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y. Khi m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&#7871;t qu&#7843; &#273;&uacute;ng (n&#259;m s&#7889; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n tr&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;u n&#259;m con s&#7889; r&uacute;t ra), c&#7847;u th&#7911; m&agrave; th&#7855;ng to&agrave;n b&#7897; Jackpot. N&oacute; c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n c&#7911;a Jackpot (1% c&#7911;a Jackpot) n&#7871;u b&#7889;n trong s&#7889; n&#259;m con s&#7889; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n tr&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;u b&#7889;n trong s&#7889; r&uacute;t ra.</p>\r\n<p>Sau m&#7897;t Jackpot &#273;&atilde; th&#7855;ng, m&#7897;t n&#7891;i m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, v&#7899;i c&aacute;c casino &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#417; s&#7903; ti&#7873;n (g&#7885;i l&agrave; h&#7841;t gi&#7889;ng). &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o r&#7857;ng ngay c&#7843; khi b&#7841;n c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t k&#7871;t qu&#7843; Jackpot trong m&#7897;t tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ngay sau khi ai &#273;&oacute; &#273;&atilde; gi&agrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot, b&#7841;n s&#7869; v&#7851;n c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng l&#7899;n.</p>\r\n<p>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>B&#7841;n ph&#7843;i th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n m&#7897;t &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c Jackpot &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n cho c&aacute;c Jackpot.</li>\r\n<li>B&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng trong v&ograve;ng &#273;&#7845;u ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&aacute;c Jackpot.</li>\r\n<li>S&#7921; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p Jackpot ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng khi b&#7841;n ch&#417;i v&#7899;i Dollar b&oacute;ng k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng paytable v&agrave; nh&acirc;n cho c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Dollar b&oacute;ng t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng v&#7899;i Jackpot ch&#7881; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u m&#7897;t Jackpot &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;ng (m&#7897;t tr&ograve; ch&#417;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&oacute;ng l&#7841;i v&agrave; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; t&#7915; c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng casino), b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&#7911;a n&oacute; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;c casino.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Jackpot cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Seed (bao nhi&ecirc;u ti&#7873;n c&#7911;a Jackpot b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&#7899;i):</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>10.000 x Jackpot c&#432;&#7907;c.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>T&#7927; l&#7879; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p (t&#7927; l&#7879; ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m c&#7911