(129, '1C', '<p><strong>5-Reel Slots 20-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a l&#7877; Ph&#7909;c Sinh Surprise l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; (&#273;&#7891;ng xu gi&aacute; tr&#7883;) c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>B&#7845;m &#273;&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i</strong> n&uacute;t gi&aacute;o ph&aacute;i &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>C&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c line. Khi s&#7889; ti&#7873;n t&#7889;i &#273;a l&agrave; &#273;&#7841;t (10 xu c&#7911;a m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n), nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset c&#432;&#7907;c line &#273;&#7875; m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu.</li>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&#7897;t payline. Khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, nh&#7845;n n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset n&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng. Payline c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c n&uacute;t s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n ph&iacute;a c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng. L&#7921;a ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t payline cao bao g&#7891;m t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p qu&aacute;. V&iacute; d&#7909;, ch&#7885;n payline 6 c&#361;ng k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 5. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet Max</strong> k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline v&#7899;i &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c t&#7889;i &#273;a cho m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng v&agrave; quay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i tr&#7853;n v&ograve;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>spin</strong> quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873; v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i. Trong gu&#7891;ng quay c&#7911;a <strong>spin</strong> thay &#273;&#7893;i th&agrave;nh n&uacute;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> . Nh&#7845;p <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong>k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ho&#7841;t h&igrave;nh spin v&agrave; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin.</li>\r\n<li>Reels c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. Nh&#7845;p + ho&#7863;c - tr&ecirc;n <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7885;n s&#7889; li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p c&#7911;a spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Auto Start</strong> quay gu&#7891;ng. C&aacute;c <strong>Auto Start</strong> n&uacute;t thay &#273;&#7893;i v&agrave;o <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> trong ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start c&#7911;a reelspin. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i, ho&#7863;c khi ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo paytable. D&ograve;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. Scatter th&#7855;ng = t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. C&aacute;c paytable c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang. Khi m&#7903; ra sau khi m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng (s&#7889; k&yacute; hi&#7879;u v&agrave; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c s&#7889; nh&acirc;n) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&aacute;nh d&#7845;u v&agrave; ch&#7899;p m&#7855;t.</li>\r\n<li>Tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ch&#7881; c&oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n khi th&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n payline kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y. Win ticker c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#7915;ng l&#7841;i b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c.</li>\r\n<li>th&#7855;ng payline v&agrave; t&#7893;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c d&#7843;i m&agrave;u &#273;en n&#7857;m &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng s&#7869; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t <strong>Gamble</strong> n&uacute;t m&agrave; khi nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o, b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Gamble. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Gamble c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trang Th&ocirc;ng tin:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Info</strong> m&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#361;i t&ecirc;n &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cho ph&eacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c nhau.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. Khi m&#7903; ra sau khi m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng (s&#7889; k&yacute; hi&#7879;u v&agrave; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c s&#7889; nh&acirc;n) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&aacute;nh d&#7845;u v&agrave; ch&#7899;p m&#7855;t.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Bonus Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c sinh</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; v&agrave;o th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c Sinh v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c Sinh.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; v&agrave;o t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Gamble</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; c&#7889; g&#7855;ng t&#259;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&aacute;nh b&#7841;c v&#7899;i h&#7885; v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c t&#259;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Hi&#7879;n Payline</strong> tr&ecirc;n <strong>paytable</strong> trang, s&#7869; m&#7903; ra m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; minh h&#7885;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline c&oacute; th&#7875;. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Hide Payline</strong> &#273;&oacute;ng m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho <strong>paytable</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>l&#7841;i</strong> tho&aacute;t ra kh&#7887;i <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p<strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i. Ti&#7873;n chung th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n l&#7841;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i l&agrave; c&aacute;c <img src="../img/eas_wild.jpg" alt="" />bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. N&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, tr&#7915; Scatter v&agrave; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t. Ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n thanh to&aacute;n ri&ecirc;ng cho hai hay nhi&#7873;u k&yacute; hi&#7879;u hoang d&atilde; tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&#432; &#273;&atilde; th&#7845;y trong paytable. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843; thay v&igrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n n&#7871;u s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; Wilds l&agrave; l&#7899;n h&#417;n so v&#7899;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n (b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7913;ng Wild).</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter <img src="../img/eas_scatter.jpg" alt="" />kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; payline c&#7909; th&#7875;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; hai ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter, &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7883; tr&iacute; n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n, trong k&#7871;t qu&#7843; quay, c&aacute;c thanh to&aacute;n thu &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o payline th&#7855;ng.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u ba ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7883; tr&iacute; n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i th&#7855;ng 10 Games mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&#7899;i s&#7889; nh&acirc;n X3 cho t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; tr&#7853;n th&#7855;ng th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c Sinh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng bonus</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u ba ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Bonus <img src="../img/eas_bonus.jpg" alt="" />xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&#7899;i c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n t&#7853;n c&ugrave;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh ho&#7863;c trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&aacute;c Bonus Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c sinh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c Sinh Bonus</strong></p>\r\n<p>&#272;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u th&#432;&#7903;ng Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c Sinh, b&#7845;m v&agrave;o <strong>Click to Start</strong> . <br />Trong Bonus Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c Sinh, ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i ph&#7843;i ch&#7885;n 3, 4 ho&#7863;c 5 tr&#7913;ng ra kh&#7887;i 6. S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#7913;ng &#273;&#7875; ch&#7885;n l&agrave; b&#7857;ng v&#7899;i s&#7889; k&yacute; hi&#7879;u ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng m&agrave; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t Ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng v&ograve;ng. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o m&#7897;t qu&#7843; tr&#7913;ng th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng ti&#7873;n m&#7863;t. C&aacute;c gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y. <br />V&agrave;o cu&#7889;i c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7897;ng d&#7891;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Nh&#7845;n <strong>Continue</strong> &#273;&#7875; tr&#7903; l&#7841;i gu&#7891;ng khe c&#7855;m th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>C&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7883; tr&iacute; n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n, k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t 10 Games mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i 3, tr&#7915; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng th&#7855;ng Tr&#7913;ng Ph&#7909;c Sinh.</p>\r\n<p>&#272;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, b&#7845;m v&agrave;o <strong>Click to Start</strong> . M&#7897;t th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o s&#7869; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n chi ti&#7871;t s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&agrave; nh&acirc;n won. Sau khi t&#7841;m d&#7915;ng ng&#7855;n, c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n xoay s&#7869; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c line nh&#432; v&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&atilde; gi&agrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. Sau m&#7895;i l&#7847;n quay, chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c. C&aacute;c <strong>tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c cho th&#7845;y ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7897;ng d&#7891;n t&#7915; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; hi&#7879;n nay.</p>\r\n<p>Sau khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ho&agrave;n t&#7845;t, m&#7897;t b&#7843;ng k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7893;ng k&#7871;t ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng. <strong>Game win</strong> th&#7875; hi&#7879;n ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7915; c&aacute;c v&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute; &#273;&atilde; th&#7855;ng c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. <strong>Feature win</strong> th&#7875; hi&#7879;n ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&atilde; nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;. <strong>T&#7893;ng s&#7889; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng</strong>cho th&#7845;y s&#7921; t&#7893;ng h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng (game Win Feature Win).</p>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c</strong> s&#7869; &#273;&#432;a b&#7841;n tr&#7903; l&#7841;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh. Khi tr&#7903; v&#7873; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh s&#7869; d&#7915;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ticker v&agrave; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; c&aacute;c gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911;. <strong>Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong> th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o payline v&agrave; Scatter th&#7855;ng.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7883; tr&iacute; n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng khi ch&#417;i Free, th&ecirc;m 10 Games mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&#7899;i h&#7879; s&#7889; t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i hi&#7879;n c&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p>Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o payline v&agrave; Scatter th&#7855;ng.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u th&#432;&#7903;ng Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i hay Ph&#7909;c Tr&#7913;ng mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t trong ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start, t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u sau khi ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o <strong>Click to Start</strong> . Khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; ho&#7863;c v&ograve;ng Bonus &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i v&agrave; nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t ch&#417;i <strong>Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c</strong> tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh t&#7893;ng k&#7871;t Tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, c&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start l&#7841;i ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c. Khi tr&#7903; v&#7873; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh s&#7869; d&#7915;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ticker v&agrave; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; c&aacute;c gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911;.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#273;&aacute;nh b&#7841;c</strong></p>\r\n<p>M&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng s&#7869; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t <strong>Gamble</strong> n&uacute;t m&agrave; khi nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o, b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Gamble, n&#417;i b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7915; v&ograve;ng xoay cu&#7889;i c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; th&#7917; v&agrave; t&#259;ng ch&uacute;ng.</p>\r\n<p>Ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong c&aacute;c <strong>Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng th&#7855;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n<strong>&#273;&#7887;</strong> ho&#7863;c <strong>&#273;en</strong> n&uacute;t. <strong>&#272;&ocirc;i &#272;&#7875;</strong> cho th&#7845;y s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&oacute; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t t&#7841;i c&aacute;c <strong>Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng</strong> , n&#7871;u b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng mu&#7889;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Thu th&#7853;p</strong> th&ecirc;m ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7915; v&ograve;ng xoay cu&#7889;i &#273;&#7875; c&acirc;n b&#7857;ng v&agrave; tr&#7903; l&#7841;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c, b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i &#273;o&aacute;n xem th&#7867; ti&#7871;p theo c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ti&#7871;t l&#7897; l&agrave; m&agrave;u &#273;&#7887; ho&#7863;c &#273;en. N&#7871;u &#273;o&aacute;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n l&agrave; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c, b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. N&#7871;u &#273;o&aacute;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n l&agrave; sai, b&#7841;n s&#7869; m&#7845;t c&#432;&#7907;c c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&agrave; c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Gamble k&#7871;t th&uacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>V&#7899;i m&#7895;i chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a cho &#273;&#7871;n khi th&#7855;ng trong <strong>Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng</strong> l&agrave; t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng ho&#7863;c l&#7899;n h&#417;n so v&#7899;i c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n Gamble. Gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ghi tr&ecirc;n <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang m&ocirc; t&#7843; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Gamble.</p>\r\n<p>Nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>Thu th&#7853;p</strong> th&ecirc;m chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; c&acirc;n b&#7857;ng v&agrave; tr&#7903; l&#7841;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> C&aacute;c <strong>Gamble</strong> n&uacute;t b&#7883; v&ocirc; hi&#7879;u h&oacute;a trong c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&agrave; trong khi <strong>Auto Start</strong> &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>N&uacute;t:</strong></p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>M&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Auto Start / Stop</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Xoay gu&#7891;ng m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&#7847;n li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p. / K&#7871;t th&uacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start reelspin ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>N&uacute;t + v&agrave; -</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>T&#259;ng ho&#7863;c gi&#7843;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin ti&#7871;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n v&#7899;i Auto Start.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>&#273;&#432;&#7901;ng</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>K&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&#7897;t payline h&#417;n.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c line.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Bet Max</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>K&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line t&#7889;i &#273;a, v&agrave; xoay gu&#7891;ng.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Spin / Stop</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Xoay gu&#7891;ng. / Trong gu&#7891;ng quay nh&#7919;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i n&uacute;t SPIN v&agrave;o STOP. Nh&#7845;p D&#7914;NG k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ho&#7841;t h&igrave;nh spin v&agrave; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin. Nh&#7845;n Stop trong ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng Auto Start k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ho&#7841;t h&igrave;nh spin v&agrave; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; reelspin Auto Start.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>&#273;&aacute;nh b&#7841;c</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&#272;&aacute;nh b&#7841;c th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c trong m&#7897;t n&#7895; l&#7921;c &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7915; spin.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; c&#7847;u th&#7911;</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&#7927; l&#7879; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i (RTP) l&agrave; 97.05%.</p>', 'vn');
