(134, '1D', '<p><strong>5-reel Slots 20-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Elektra l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>M&#7897;t c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; (&#273;&#7891;ng xu gi&aacute; tr&#7883;) c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o <strong>B&#7845;m &#273;&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i</strong> n&uacute;t gi&aacute;o ph&aacute;i &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</li>\r\n<li>C&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t xu v&agrave;o c&#432;&#7907;c line. Khi s&#7889; ti&#7873;n t&#7889;i &#273;a l&agrave; &#273;&#7841;t (10 xu c&#7911;a m&#7879;nh gi&aacute; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n), nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset c&#432;&#7907;c line &#273;&#7875; m&#7897;t &#273;&#7891;ng xu.</li>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> . M&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7845;p l&agrave; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&#7897;t payline. Khi t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, nh&#7845;n n&uacute;t m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a reset n&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng. Payline c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c n&uacute;t s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n ph&iacute;a c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng. L&#7921;a ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t payline cao bao g&#7891;m t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p qu&aacute;. V&iacute; d&#7909;, ch&#7885;n payline 6 c&#361;ng k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 5.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i tr&#7853;n v&ograve;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>spin</strong> quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873; v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i. Trong gu&#7891;ng quay c&#7911;a <strong>spin</strong> thay &#273;&#7893;i th&agrave;nh n&uacute;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> . Nh&#7845;p <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong>k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ho&#7841;t h&igrave;nh spin v&agrave; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin.</li>\r\n<li>Reels c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. Nh&#7845;p + ho&#7863;c - tr&ecirc;n <strong>Auto Start</strong> ch&#7885;n s&#7889; li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p c&#7911;a spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Auto Start</strong> quay gu&#7891;ng. C&aacute;c <strong>Auto Start</strong> n&uacute;t thay &#273;&#7893;i v&agrave;o <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> trong ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start c&#7911;a reelspin. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Start s&#7869; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i, ho&#7863;c khi ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo paytable. D&ograve;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. Scatter th&#7855;ng = t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. C&aacute;c paytable c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ch&#7881; c&oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n khi th&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n payline kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y. Win ticker c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#7915;ng l&#7841;i b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c.</li>\r\n<li>th&#7855;ng payline v&agrave; t&#7893;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; tr&ecirc;n d&#7843;i n&#7857;m &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a cu&#7897;n ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trang Th&ocirc;ng tin:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Info</strong> m&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#361;i t&ecirc;n &#7903; g&oacute;c d&#432;&#7899;i b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cho ph&eacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c nhau.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. Khi m&#7903; ra sau khi m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng (s&#7889; k&yacute; hi&#7879;u v&agrave; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c s&#7889; nh&acirc;n) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&aacute;nh d&#7845;u v&agrave; ch&#7899;p m&#7855;t.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Bonus</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t c&#7911;a c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7875; v&agrave;o v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c v&ograve;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng.</li>\r\n<li><strong>V&#361; kh&iacute; Bonus</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; ba l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#361; kh&iacute; v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Marvel Multi-Level B&iacute; &#7849;n Progressive Jackpot</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh v&agrave;o Marvel Multi-Level B&iacute; &#7849;n Progressive Jackpot tr&ograve; ch&#417;i m&agrave; th&#7855;ng m&#7897;t trong b&#7889;n gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li><strong>Hi&#7879;n Payline</strong> c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7845;p t&#7915; trang paytable &#273;&#7875; m&#7903; ra m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh minh h&#7885;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline c&oacute; th&#7875;. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Hide Payline</strong> &#273;&oacute;ng m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho <strong>paytable</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>l&#7841;i</strong> tho&aacute;t ra kh&#7887;i <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p<strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; cho quy t&#7855;c n&agrave;y. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong> C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;u v&ograve;ng. To&aacute;n t&#7927; l&#7879; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line. M&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; l&agrave; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter, m&agrave; chung ti&#7873;n hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho m&#7895;i payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&oacute; m&#7897;t k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng tr&ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t gu&#7891;ng, ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; gu&#7891;ng b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n l&#7841;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i l&agrave; c&aacute;c <img src="../img/elektra_sym0.jpg" alt="" />bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. N&oacute; ch&#7881; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n # 2, # 3 v&agrave; # 4 v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, tr&#7915; Scatter, &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M&#7903; r&#7897;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u m&#7897;t bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng hoang d&atilde; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t cu&#7897;n sau khi m&#7897;t tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; c&oacute; m&#7897;t k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c c&oacute; m&#7897;t thay hoang d&atilde; cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c (tr&#7915; Scatter) b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n cu&#7897;n &#273;&oacute;, n&oacute; s&#7869; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng &#273;&#7875; bao g&#7891;m to&agrave;n b&#7897; gu&#7891;ng. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c n&#417;i tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&agrave; hoang d&atilde; cho quay m&#7897;t m&igrave;nh. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng l&agrave; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; c&#7911;a &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thanh to&aacute;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i l&agrave; c&aacute;c <img src="../img/elektra_sym12.jpg" alt="" />bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng. C&aacute;c Scatter kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline c&#7909; th&#7875; - n&#7871;u c&oacute; hai hay nhi&#7873;u k&yacute; hi&#7879;u ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n trong c&aacute;c k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin, m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&ecirc;m l&agrave; ki&#7871;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. Vi&#7879;c thanh to&aacute;n cho nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. N&#7871;u 3 ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, b&#7845;t k&#7875; v&#7883; tr&iacute;, v&#361; kh&iacute; th&#432;&#7903;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u.</p>\r\n<p>N&#7871;u ba ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng khi ch&#417;i Free, ch&#7881; thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao nh&#432;ng ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng v&ograve;ng s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&aacute;i k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#361; kh&iacute; Bonus game</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c v&#361; kh&iacute; Bonus v&ograve;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t khi ba ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. &#272;&#7875; nh&#7853;p ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng v&ograve;ng, b&#7845;m v&agrave;o <strong>Click to Start</strong> . B&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t trong ba lo&#7841;i v&#361; kh&iacute;, m&#7895;i cung c&#7845;p m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&aacute;c nhau c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&agrave; m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng nh&acirc;n kh&aacute;c nhau. M&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; b&#7845;t k&#7923; chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; &#273;&oacute;. &#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>S&agrave;i Swords: 10 tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;</li>\r\n<li>Shuriken: 14 tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&#7899;i s&#7889; nh&acirc;n X2</li>\r\n<li>Bow v&agrave; Arrow: 7 tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; v&#7899;i s&#7889; nh&acirc;n X4</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Sau khi l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n, c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u.</p>\r\n<p>Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&#432;&#7907;c line, k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7891;ng xu v&agrave; s&#7889; d&ograve;ng l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng ch&#417;i.</p>\r\n<p>Trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a c&aacute;c v&#361; kh&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n s&#7869; thay th&#7871; tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n hai bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#361; kh&iacute; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&agrave; s&#7869; tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n theo paytable c&#7911;a bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&oacute;. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Wild trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng hoang d&atilde; (xem &#7903; tr&ecirc;n).</p>\r\n<p>V&agrave;o cu&#7889;i c&#7911;a tr&ograve; ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute;, m&#7897;t m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t chi ti&#7871;t c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng th&#7855;ng xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n. &#272;&#7875; tr&#7903; l&#7841;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh, nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c</strong> .</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot l&agrave; m&#7897;t &#273;a c&#7845;p ti&#7871;n b&#7897; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i jackpot m&agrave; c&oacute; s&#7861;n trong t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&#7899;i t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel.M&#7897;t t&#7927; l&#7879; nh&#7887; c&#7911;a m&#7895;i c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel, b&#7903;i m&#7895;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y trong m&#7895;i nhi&#7873;u s&ograve;ng b&#7841;c tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o jackpot l&#361;y ti&#7871;n.</p>\r\n<p>Vi&#7879;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t m&agrave; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot l&agrave; ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; x&#7843;y ra sau khi b&#7845;t k&#7923; quay trong b&#7845;t k&#7923; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t. N&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; do b&#7845;t k&#7923; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&agrave; th&#7853;m ch&iacute; m&#7897;t spin m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7845;t c&#7913; &#273;i&#7873;u g&igrave; trong tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; v&#7853;y, b&#7845;t k&#7923; c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t c&oacute; th&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot.Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c&#417; h&#7897;i k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i t&#259;ng Jackpot ho&#7863;c gi&#7843;m t&#7927; l&#7879; thu&#7853;n v&#7899;i m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c. B&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#7911;a m&#7897;t trong b&#7889;n gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t. Ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Jackpot ti&#7871;t l&#7897; jackpot &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trao cho b&#7841;n, nh&#432;ng kh&ocirc;ng x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh n&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p>C&oacute; b&#7889;n c&#7845;p &#273;&#7897; kh&aacute;c nhau c&#7911;a gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t m&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng: Power Jackpot, Extra Power Jackpot, Super Power Jackpot v&agrave; Ultimate &#273;i&#7879;n Jackpot. C&aacute;c lo&#7841;i kh&aacute;c nhau c&#7911;a gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t n&#7855;m gi&#7919; m&#7897;t l&#432;&#7907;ng gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng kh&aacute;c nhau. C&aacute;c gamescreen jackpot ch&#7913;a 20 h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng m&agrave; trong &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i &#273;ang b&#7883; &#273;&#7843;o l&#7897;n. Nh&#7845;p chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o m&#7897;t h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng s&#7869; bi&#7871;n n&oacute; xung quanh v&agrave; ti&#7871;t l&#7897; m&#7897;t trong b&#7889;n bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&#7855;c &#7903; ph&iacute;a b&ecirc;n kia. M&#7897;t khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; t&igrave;m th&#7845;y ba bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p, b&#7841;n gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng trong jackpot t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng v&#7899;i c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng n&agrave;y. Tr&uacute;ng th&#432;&#7903;ng Jackpot &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o th&#7855;ng tr&ograve; ch&#417;i ch&iacute;nh (n&#7871;u c&oacute;) v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; trong <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; th&#7855;ng kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot tr&ograve; ch&#417;i c&oacute; m&#7897;t gi&#7901; th&#7901;i gian ch&#7901;. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; ngh&#297;a r&#7857;ng n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng trong m&#7897;t kho&#7843;ng th&#7901;i gian, b&#7841;n s&#7869; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i th&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p>\r\n<p>The Jackpot cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i n&agrave;y ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Seed</strong> (bao nhi&ecirc;u ti&#7873;n c&#7911;a Gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&#7899;i):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Power: 50 &euro; <br />Extra Power: 500 &euro; <br />Super Power: 5000 &euro; <br />cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng Power: 100.000 &euro;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>T&#7927; l&#7879; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p</strong> (t&#7927; l&#7879; ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m c&#7911;a m&#7895;i c&aacute; c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i v&agrave;o Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>0.99%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Win &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n</strong> (c&aacute;c k&#7871;t qu&#7843; m&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7875; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&aacute;c Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>B&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o tr&ograve; ch&#417;i jackpot &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o m&#7897;t chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. c&aacute;c k&yacute; hi&#7879;u Match 3 jackpot c&#7911;a Jackpot t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng ho&#7863;c ch&#7901; &#273;&#7907;i cho b&#7897; &#273;&#7871;m th&#7901;i gian ch&#7841;y ra ngo&agrave;i.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u Win</strong> (nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; b&#7841;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i l&agrave;m g&igrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n cho c&aacute;c Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Ch&#417;i m&#7897;t tr&ograve; ch&#417;i Marvel.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Xin l&#432;u &yacute;:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; gi&#7889;ng v&agrave; Jackpot l&agrave; &#273;&#7891;ng Euro trong m&#7841;ng ti&#7871;n b&#7897; v&agrave; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a h&#7885; trong ti&#7873;n t&#7879; &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n l&agrave; ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o t&#7927; gi&aacute; h&#7889;i &#273;o&aacute;i.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c c&#417; ch&#7871; c&#7911;a Marvel B&iacute; &#7849;n Jackpot c&#7845;m th&#7855;ng jackpot &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i.</li>\r\n<li>Kh&ocirc;ng ho&agrave;n h&#7843;o trong k&#7871;t n&#7889;i Internet c&oacute; th&#7875; g&acirc;y ra c&aacute;c b&#7841;n tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m s&#7921; ch&#7853;m tr&#7877; trong c&aacute;c tin nh&#7855;n Jackpot ho&#7863;c c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t, nh&#432;ng h&#7885; kh&ocirc;ng &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; Jackpot th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Quay tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; c&#7847;u th&#7911;</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&#7927; l&#7879; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i (RTP) l&agrave; 94,94%.</p>', 'vn');
INSERT INTO `ep_translations` (`game_trans_id`, `game_id`, `game_details`, `game_lang`) VALUES
(135, '1E', '<p><strong>5-reel 25-line slots</strong></p>\r\n<p>The objective of Esmeralda is to obtain winning symbol combinations by spinning the reels.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To play the game:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Line bets are chosen by clicking + and &ndash; below <strong>Line Bet</strong> to increase or decrease the amount.</li>\r\n<li>Paylines can be activated and their shape displayed by progressively clicking + and &ndash; below <strong>Lines</strong>. Paylines can also be activated by using the numbered buttons on either side of the reels. Selecting a high payline includes all the lower ones too. For example, selecting payline 6 also activates paylines 1 through 5. Clicking <strong>Bet Max</strong> activates all paylines with the currently selected bet per line and spins the reels.</li>\r\n<li>Total bet per game round = line bet X active paylines.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Spin</strong> spins the reels with the current selection of lines and line bets. During the reel spins the <strong>Spin</strong> button changes into<strong>Stop</strong>. Clicking<strong>Stop</strong> ends the spin animation and immediately displays the spin result.</li>\r\n<li>Reels can also be spun using the <strong>Auto Play</strong> function. Mouse over the <strong>Auto Play</strong> button to display the list of options. Select the number of spins to be played automatically or choose &lsquo;Until Feature&rsquo; to spin until the Free Games round is triggered. Clicking on an option starts the Auto Play function. The <strong>Auto Play</strong> button changes into <strong>Stop</strong> during the Auto Play mode. The Auto Play mode ends when the reels have been spun the number of times determined by the player, or when a Free Games round is triggered if you chose &lsquo;Until Feature&rsquo;, or when you click <strong>Stop</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Clicking the <strong>Turbo Mode</strong> button switches on or off the Turbo Mode thus turning on or off some of the win animations and sounds, and making the reels spin faster or slower.</li>\r\n<li>Wins are calculated according to the paytable. Line win = line bet X corresponding multiplier according to the paytable. Scatter win = total bet X corresponding multiplier according to the paytable. The paytable can be accessed via the <strong>Info</strong> page.</li>\r\n<li>On a given payline, only the highest payline winning combination pays while simultaneous winnings on different paylines are accumulated.</li>\r\n<li>In case of a winning spin, the <strong>Win</strong> field displays the accumulating winnings. The Win ticker can be stopped by clicking anywhere on the screen to display the total win amount immediately.</li>\r\n<li>Payline wins and the total win are also displayed on the strip located at the bottom of the reels or the game window.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Info page:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Info</strong> opens the reference screen describing different game components. Clicking the arrow buttons at the bottom of the screen enables navigating between the different info screens.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paytable</strong> screen shows all winning combinations. When opened after a winning spin, the awarded multiplier is highlighted and blinks.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Jackpot</strong> screen explains the rules of the Progressive Jackpot, describes how the Jackpot is triggered and how to qualify for the Jackpot.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Double</strong> screen describes how to try doubling winnings and describes the doubling-up rules.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paylines</strong> screen illustrates all possible payline combinations and explains the payout rules in the game.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Clicking <strong>Exit</strong> exits the <strong>Info</strong> screen and returns to the game.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Active paylines are represented by lines that appear over the reels. Paylines can be activated and their shape displayed by progressively clicking + or &ndash; below <strong>Lines</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Only active paylines can register wins.</li>\r\n<li>There is a difference between the line bet and the total bet. The line bet shows how much is being bet on a single payline. The total bet shows how much is being bet in total on the game round. Payouts shown in the paytable are multiplied by the line bet.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Scatter symbol is an exception to these rules. More information about the Scatter symbol can be found below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About payouts:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payouts are listed on the <strong>Paytable</strong> screen. To find the possible win amount, the line bet must be multiplied by the payout.</li>\r\n<li>If two payline winning combinations occur on the same line, the higher of them is paid out. If more than one active payline has a winning combination, the winnings are accumulated.</li>\r\n<li>Winning combinations must start from the left most reel, and the symbols have to be consecutive.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Scatter symbol is an exception to these rules. More information about the Scatter symbol can be found below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Wild Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Wild symbol <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" /> appears anywhere on reels. During the main game, it can stand for any other symbol, except Scatter, to make the best possible winning combination. During the Free Games, <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" /> also substitutes for <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" />. There is also a separate payout for three or more Wild symbols on an active payline, as shown in the paytable.</p>\r\n<p>Five Wilds on an active payline trigger the Progressive Jackpot if qualified or pay the max win according to the paytable if the player does not qualify for the Jackpot. More information about the Progressive Jackpot can be found below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Scatter Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Scatter symbols <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" /> do not have to occur on any particular payline. 5, 6 or 7 Scatters anywhere on reels pay winnings multiplied by 2x total bet.</p>\r\n<p>8 to 15 Scatters appearing simultaneously anywhere on the reels during the main game trigger 15, 17, 19, 20, 22, 25, 35 or 70 Free Games respectively and pay separately; the winnings are multiplied by the total bet as described in the paytable.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Jackpot</strong></p>\r\n<p>One of the possible wins in this game is the Progressive Jackpot, built up by all the casinos that offer the game. A small percentage of each bet, by every person that qualifies for the Jackpot and plays this game in each of many online casinos, is added to a common pot. When a player gets the right result, that player wins the entire Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>After a Jackpot has been won, a new pot is started, with a guaranteed minimum amount of money (called a seed). This ensures that even if you get a Jackpot result in a game right after someone else has won the Jackpot, you will still get a large win.</p>\r\n<p>In this game, a player is qualified to win the Progressive Jackpot if playing with maximum number of active paylines (25) and betting with the highest possible coin size. Players only contribute to the progressive pot and the seed pot if they qualify for the Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>The Jackpot for this game works like this:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Seed</strong> (how much money the Jackpot starts out with):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>25,000 x line bet</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Contribution rate</strong> (what percentage of each bet goes into the Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>1.7%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Win condition</strong> (the result you have to get to win the Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>5 Wild symbols on an active payline.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Win requirements</strong> (what you need to do to be eligible for the Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Play Esmeralda slot game with maximum number of active paylines and the highest coin size.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>If you get disconnected in the middle of a game round, your game does not change the value of the Jackpot. The state of the game up to that point is remembered by the casino; the next time you log in you can finish your game round with the same odds and without placing a new bet.</li>\r\n<li>If a Jackpot is being discontinued (a game is closed and removed from the casino client), you will be notified of it by the casino.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Free Games</strong></p>\r\n<p>15, 17, 19, 20, 22, 25, 35 or 70 Free Games are triggered by the appearance of 8 to 15 <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" /> respectively during the main game. To start the Free Games, click on <strong>Click to Start</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Three to five <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" /> symbols anywhere on reels during the Free Games pay according to the paytable. Five Wilds on an active payline trigger the Progressive Jackpot if qualified or pay the max win according to the paytable if the player does not qualify for the Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>Five to seven <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" /> symbols, including <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" /> symbols substituting for Scatter symbols anywhere on reels during the Free Games, pay according to the paytable. Eight or more <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" /> symbols, including <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" /> symbols substituting for Scatter symbols, add more Free Games as described above. More Free Games can be won this way infinitely.</p>\r\n<p>During the Free Games, the reels are spun automatically using the same number of lines and bets per line as on the spin that won the Free Games round. After each spin, the win is displayed in the <strong>Win</strong> field. The <strong>Free Games Win</strong> field shows the accumulated winnings from the current Free Games.</p>\r\n<p>After all Free Games have been completed, a result board summarizes the winnings and states the number of Free Games played.<strong>Feature win</strong>shows the winnings that were received during the Free Games. Clicking on the board will return you to the main game.</p>\r\n<p>When returning to the main game, clicking anywhere on the screen stops the win ticker and displays the full prize. Free Game wins are added to the payline and Scatter wins.</p>\r\n<p>If the Free Games that follow have been triggered during the Auto Play mode, the Free Games round begins after the player clicks on<strong>Click to Start</strong>. When all Free Games have been played and the player clicks on the screen summarizing the Free Games win, the Auto Play mode resumes. When returning to the main game, clicking anywhere on the screen stops the win ticker and displays the full prize.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Double</strong></p>\r\n<p>A win activates the <strong>Double</strong> button which, when clicked, starts the Double feature where you can bet the winnings from your last spin to try to increase them.</p>\r\n<p>Your current winnings are shown in the <strong>Bank</strong> field. You can choose to bet these winnings by clicking the <strong>Double</strong> button. The <strong>Double To</strong>field shows the amount that will be placed in the Bank if you win. <br />You can also choose to bet only half of your current winnings (by clicking <strong>Double Half</strong>) and keep the other half in the Bank. The <strong>Double Half To</strong> field shows the amount that will be placed in the Bank (includes the amount that remained in the Bank) if you win. <br />The <strong>Bet</strong> field will show your bet in the Double round.</p>\r\n<p>If you do not want to bet, you can click <strong>Collect</strong> to add the winnings from the last spin to your balance and return to the main game. If you choose to bet, the dealer&rsquo;s card is revealed on the left-hand side of the screen and you have to pick a card from the remaining face-down cards. If you pick a card with a higher ranking than the dealer&rsquo;s card, you win. If your card is equal in ranking, the bet is returned. If your card is lower in ranking than the dealer&rsquo;s card, you lose your bet and the Double feature ends.</p>\r\n<p>With every win, you can bet again until the winnings in the Bank are equal to or greater than the Double feature limit. The limit is shown on the <strong>Info</strong>page that describes the Double feature.</p>\r\n<p>Click <strong>Collect</strong> to add your winnings from the Bank to your balance and return to the main game.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong> The <strong>Double</strong> button is disabled during the Free Games and while the Auto Play is active.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Return to Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>The theoretical percentage return to player (RTP) is 94.06% + 1.7% when qualified for the Progressive Jackpot and 94.16% when not qualified for the Progressive Jackpot.</p>', 'en'),
(136, '1E', '<p><strong>5-reel slot 25-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tujuan dari Esmeralda adalah untuk mendapatkan kombinasi simbol menang dengan memutar reel.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Untuk memainkan permainan:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Taruhan baris yang dipilih dengan mengklik + dan - di bawah <strong>garis Bet</strong> untuk menambah atau mengurangi jumlah.</li>\r\n<li>Paylines dapat diaktifkan dan bentuk mereka ditampilkan dengan mengklik + dan - di bawah <strong>Garis</strong> . Paylines juga dapat diaktifkan dengan menggunakan tombol bernomor pada kedua sisi reel. Memilih payline tinggi mencakup semua yang lebih rendah juga. Misalnya, memilih payline 6 juga mengaktifkan paylines 1 sampai 5. Mengklik <strong>Bet Max</strong> mengaktifkan semua paylines dengan taruhan saat ini dipilih per baris dan berputar gulungan.</li>\r\n<li>Total taruhan per game putaran = taruhan garis X paylines aktif.</li>\r\n<li><span class="goog-text-highlight">Mengklik </span><strong><span class="goog-text-highlight">spin</span></strong><span class="goog-text-highlight"> berputar gulungan dengan pilihan saat ini dari garis dan garis taruhan. </span>Selama reel berputar <strong>spin</strong> tombol berubah menjadi<strong>Berhenti</strong> . Mengklik <strong>Berhenti</strong> mengakhiri animasi berputar dan langsung menampilkan hasil spin.</li>\r\n<li>Gulungan juga dapat berputar menggunakan <strong>Auto Play</strong> fungsi. Mouse pada <strong>Auto Play</strong> tombol untuk menampilkan daftar pilihan. Pilih jumlah berputar untuk dimainkan secara otomatis atau memilih ''Sampai Fitur'' berputar hingga babak Free Games dipicu. Mengklik pada opsi mulai fungsi Auto Play. The <strong>Auto Putar</strong> tombol berubah menjadi <strong>Berhenti</strong> selama modus Auto Play. Modus Auto Play berakhir ketika gulungan telah berputar jumlah kali ditentukan oleh pemain, atau saat putaran Free Games dipicu jika Anda memilih ''Sampai Fitur'', atau ketika Anda klik<strong>Berhenti</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Turbo Mode</strong> tombol switch atau menonaktifkan Turbo Mode sehingga menyalakan atau mematikan beberapa animasi menang dan suara, dan membuat gulungan berputar lebih cepat atau lebih lambat.</li>\r\n<li>Menang dihitung berdasarkan paytable tersebut. Garis menang taruhan garis X = multiplier yang sesuai menurut paytable. Pencar win = total taruhan X multiplier yang sesuai menurut paytable. Paytable dapat diakses melalui <strong>Info</strong> halaman.</li>\r\n<li>Pada payline diberikan, hanya tertinggi kombinasi payline menang membayar sementara kemenangan simultan pada paylines yang berbeda diakumulasi.</li>\r\n<li>Dalam kasus spin menang, <strong>Win</strong> bidang menampilkan kemenangan terakumulasi. Win ticker dapat dihentikan dengan mengklik di manapun pada layar untuk menampilkan jumlah total menang segera.</li>\r\n<li>menang payline dan menang total juga ditampilkan pada strip yang terletak di bagian bawah gulungan atau jendela permainan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Halaman Info:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Info</strong> membuka layar referensi yang menggambarkan komponen permainan yang berbeda. Mengklik tombol panah di bagian bawah layar memungkinkan navigasi antara layar berbagai info.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paytable</strong> layar menunjukkan semua kombinasi pemenang. Ketika dibuka setelah spin menang, multiplier diberikan disorot dan berkedip.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Jackpot</strong> layar menjelaskan aturan Progressive Jackpot, menggambarkan bagaimana Jackpot dipicu dan bagaimana untuk memenuhi syarat untuk Jackpot.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Dua</strong> Layar menjelaskan bagaimana untuk mencoba menggandakan kemenangan dan menjelaskan aturan menggandakan-up.</li>\r\n<li>The <strong>Paylines</strong> layar menggambarkan semua kombinasi payline mungkin dan menjelaskan aturan pembayaran dalam permainan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Mengklik <strong>Exit</strong> keluar dari <strong>Info</strong> layar dan kembali ke permainan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>paylines:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Paylines aktif diwakili oleh garis-garis yang muncul di atas gulungan. Paylines dapat diaktifkan dan bentuk mereka ditampilkan dengan mengklik + atau - di bawah <strong>Garis</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Hanya paylines aktif dapat mendaftar menang.</li>\r\n<li>Ada perbedaan antara garis taruhan dan total taruhan. Taruhan garis menunjukkan berapa banyak yang bertaruh pada payline tunggal. Total taruhan menunjukkan berapa banyak yang bertaruh secara total pada putaran permainan. Pembayaran ditampilkan dalam paytable dikalikan dengan taruhan baris.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Simbol Scatter merupakan pengecualian aturan ini. Informasi lebih lanjut tentang simbol Scatter dapat ditemukan di bawah.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tentang pembayaran:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pembayaran tercatat di <strong>Paytable</strong> layar. Untuk menemukan jumlah menang mungkin, garis taruhan harus dikalikan dengan payout.</li>\r\n<li>Jika dua kombinasi pemenang payline terjadi pada baris yang sama, lebih tinggi dari mereka dibayarkan. Jika lebih dari satu payline aktif memiliki kombinasi menang, kemenangan diakumulasikan.</li>\r\n<li>Kombinasi pemenang harus mulai dari gulungan paling kiri, dan simbol harus berturut-turut.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Simbol Scatter merupakan pengecualian aturan ini. Informasi lebih lanjut tentang simbol Scatter dapat ditemukan di bawah.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Simbol wild</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simbol liar <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" />muncul di mana saja pada gulungan. Selama permainan utama, dapat berdiri untuk setiap simbol lain, kecuali scatter, untuk membuat kombinasi pemenang terbaik. Selama Game Gratis, <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" />juga pengganti untuk <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" />. Ada juga pembayaran terpisah untuk tiga atau lebih simbol Wild pada payline aktif, seperti yang ditunjukkan dalam paytable.</p>\r\n<p>Lima Wilds pada payline pemicu aktif Progressive Jackpot jika memenuhi syarat atau membayar kemenangan max menurut paytable jika pemain tidak memenuhi syarat untuk Jackpot. Informasi lebih lanjut tentang Progressive Jackpot dapat ditemukan di bawah.</p>\r\n<p><strong>pencar Symbol</strong></p>\r\n<p>The simbol Scatter <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" />tidak harus terjadi pada setiap payline tertentu. 5, 6 atau 7 Scatter manapun pada gulungan membayar kemenangan dikalikan dengan total taruhan 2x.</p>\r\n<p>8 sampai 15 Scatter muncul secara bersamaan di manapun pada gulungan selama pertandingan pemicu utama 15, 17, 19, 20, 22, 25, 35 atau 70 Game masing-masing dan membayar secara terpisah; kemenangan yang dikalikan dengan total taruhan seperti yang dijelaskan dalam paytable.</p>\r\n<p><strong>hadiah main kartu</strong></p>\r\n<p>Salah satu kemenangan mungkin dalam permainan ini adalah Progressive Jackpot, dibangun oleh semua kasino yang menawarkan permainan.Sebagian kecil masing-masing taruhan, oleh setiap orang yang memenuhi syarat untuk Jackpot dan memainkan game ini di masing-masing banyak kasino online, ditambahkan ke pot umum. Ketika seorang pemain mendapat hasil yang tepat, pemain yang memenangkan seluruh Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>Setelah Jackpot telah dimenangkan, pot baru dimulai, dengan jumlah minimum yang dijamin uang (disebut benih). Hal ini memastikan bahwa bahkan jika Anda mendapatkan hasil Jackpot dalam permainan segera setelah seseorang telah memenangkan Jackpot, Anda masih akan mendapatkan kemenangan yang besar.</p>\r\n<p>Dalam game ini, pemain yang memenuhi syarat untuk memenangkan Progressive Jackpot jika bermain dengan jumlah maksimum paylines aktif (25) dan taruhan dengan kemungkinan ukuran koin tertinggi. Pemain hanya berkontribusi pada pot progresif dan pot unggulan jika mereka lolos ke Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>Jackpot untuk permainan ini bekerja seperti ini:</p>\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Benih</strong> (berapa banyak uang Jackpot dimulai dengan):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>25.000 x taruhan baris</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Tingkat kontribusi</strong> (persentase masing-masing taruhan masuk ke Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>1,7%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Kondisi Win</strong> (hasil Anda harus mendapatkan untuk memenangkan Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>5 simbol Wild pada payline aktif.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Persyaratan Win</strong> (apa yang harus Anda lakukan untuk memenuhi persyaratan untuk Jackpot):</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Bermain Esmeralda Slot permainan dengan jumlah maksimum paylines aktif dan ukuran koin tertinggi.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Tolong dicatat:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Jika Anda terputus di tengah putaran permainan, permainan Anda tidak mengubah nilai Jackpot. Keadaan permainan sampai titik yang diingat oleh kasino; pada saat Anda login Anda dapat menyelesaikan putaran permainan Anda dengan peluang yang sama dan tanpa menempatkan taruhan baru.</li>\r\n<li>Jika Jackpot sedang dihentikan (permainan ditutup dan dihapus dari klien kasino), Anda akan diberitahu dengan kasino.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Permainan gratis</strong></p>\r\n<p>15, 17, 19, 20, 22, 25, 35 atau 70 Game Gratis dipicu oleh munculnya 8 sampai 15 <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" />masing-masing selama pertandingan utama. Untuk memulai Game Gratis, klik <strong>Click to Start</strong> .</p>\r\n<p>Tiga sampai lima <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" />simbol di mana saja pada gulungan selama Game Gratis membayar sesuai dengan paytable. Lima Wilds pada payline pemicu aktif Progressive Jackpot jika memenuhi syarat atau membayar kemenangan max menurut paytable jika pemain tidak memenuhi syarat untuk Jackpot.</p>\r\n<p>Lima sampai tujuh <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" />simbol, termasuk <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" />simbol menggantikan simbol Scatter mana saja di gulungan selama Game Gratis, membayar sesuai dengan paytable. Delapan atau lebih <img src="../img/esm_scatter.jpg" alt="" />simbol, termasuk <img src="../img/esm_wild.jpg" alt="" />simbol menggantikan simbol Scatter, menambahkan lebih banyak Gratis Permainan seperti dijelaskan di atas. Lebih Gratis Permainan dapat dimenangkan dengan cara ini jauh.</p>\r\n<p>Selama Game Gratis, gulungan yang berputar secara otomatis dengan menggunakan nomor yang sama dan taruhan baris per baris seperti pada spin yang memenangkan putaran gratis Game. Setelah setiap putaran, kemenangan ditampilkan di <strong>Win</strong> bidang. The <strong>Free Games Win</strong> lapangan menunjukkan kemenangan akumulasi dari Free Games saat ini.</p>\r\n<p>Setelah semua Game Gratis telah selesai, papan merangkum hasil kemenangan dan menyatakan jumlah Free Games dimainkan. <strong>Fitur menang</strong>menunjukkan kemenangan yang diterima selama Olimpiade gratis. Mengklik pada papan Anda akan kembali ke permainan utama.</p>\r\n<p>Ketika kembali ke permainan utama, klik di mana saja pada layar berhenti ticker menang dan menampilkan hadiah penuh. menang permainan gratis ditambahkan ke payline dan Menyebarkan menang.</p>\r\n<p>Jika Game Gratis yang mengikuti telah dipicu selama modus Auto Play, babak Free Games dimulai setelah pemain mengklik <strong>Click to Start</strong> . Ketika semua Game Gratis telah dimainkan dan pemain klik pada layar meringkas menang Game Gratis, modus Auto Play resume. Ketika kembali ke permainan utama, klik di mana saja pada layar berhenti ticker menang dan menampilkan hadiah penuh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dua kali lipat</strong></p>\r\n<p>Kemenangan mengaktifkan <strong>dua</strong> tombol yang, ketika diklik, memulai fitur ganda di mana Anda bisa bertaruh kemenangan dari spin terakhir Anda untuk mencoba untuk meningkatkan mereka.</p>\r\n<p>Kemenangan Anda saat ini akan ditampilkan di <strong>Bank</strong> lapangan. Anda dapat memilih untuk bertaruh kemenangan ini dengan mengklik <strong>ganda</strong>tombol. The <strong>Ganda Untuk</strong> lapangan menunjukkan jumlah yang akan ditempatkan di Bank jika Anda menang. <br />Anda juga dapat memilih untuk bertaruh hanya setengah dari kemenangan Anda saat ini (dengan mengklik <strong>ganda Half</strong> ) dan menjaga separuh lainnya di Bank. The <strong>Half ganda Untuk</strong> lapangan menunjukkan jumlah yang akan ditempatkan di Bank (termasuk jumlah yang tetap di Bank) jika Anda menang. <br />The <strong>Bet</strong> lapangan akan menunjukkan taruhan Anda di babak dua.</p>\r\n<p>Jika Anda tidak ingin bertaruh, Anda dapat klik <strong>Collect</strong> untuk menambah kemenangan dari spin terakhir untuk saldo Anda dan kembali ke permainan utama. Jika Anda memilih untuk bertaruh, kartu dealer terungkap di sisi kiri layar dan Anda harus memilih kartu dari wajah-bawah kartu yang tersisa.Jika Anda memilih kartu dengan peringkat yang lebih tinggi daripada kartu Dealer, Anda menang. Jika kartu Anda adalah sama dalam peringkat, taruhan dikembalikan. Jika kartu Anda lebih rendah dalam peringkat daripada kartu Dealer, Anda kehilangan taruhan Anda dan fitur ganda berakhir.</p>\r\n<p>Dengan setiap kemenangan, Anda dapat bertaruh lagi sampai kemenangan di Bank adalah sama dengan atau lebih besar dari batas fitur ganda.Batas yang ditampilkan pada <strong>Info</strong> halaman yang menjelaskan fitur ganda.</p>\r\n<p>Klik <strong>Kumpulkan</strong> menambah kemenangan dari Bank ke saldo Anda dan kembali ke permainan utama.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Harap dicatat:</strong> The <strong>Dua</strong> tombol dinonaktifkan selama Olimpiade gratis dan sementara Auto Play aktif.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kembali ke Player</strong></p>\r\n<p>Teoritis persentase kembali ke pemain (RTP) adalah 94,06% + 1,7% ketika lolos ke Progressive Jackpot dan 94,16% bila tidak memenuhi syarat untuk Progressive Jackpot.</p>', 'id');
INSERT INTO `ep_translations` (`game_trans_id`, `game_id`, `game_details`, `game_lang`) VALUES
(137, '1E', '<p><strong>5-reel khe c&#7855;m 25-line</strong></p>\r\n<p>M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a Esmeralda l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&#272;&#7875; ch&#417;i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;p + v&agrave; - b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>d&ograve;ng Bet</strong> &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng ho&#7863;c gi&#7843;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng.</li>\r\n<li>Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p + v&agrave; - b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> . Payline c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c n&uacute;t s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n ph&iacute;a c&#7911;a gu&#7891;ng. L&#7921;a ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t payline cao bao g&#7891;m t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7845;p qu&aacute;. V&iacute; d&#7909;, ch&#7885;n payline 6 c&#361;ng k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t payline t&#7915; 1 &#273;&#7871;n 5. Nh&#7845;p <strong>Bet Max</strong> k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t t&#7845;t c&#7843; payline v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n tr&ecirc;n m&#7895;i d&ograve;ng v&agrave; quay gu&#7891;ng.</li>\r\n<li>T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c m&#7895;i tr&#7853;n v&ograve;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n.</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>spin</strong> quay c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n v&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873; v&agrave; c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i. Trong gu&#7891;ng quay c&#7911;a <strong>spin</strong> thay &#273;&#7893;i th&agrave;nh n&uacute;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> . Nh&#7845;p <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong>k&#7871;t th&uacute;c ho&#7841;t h&igrave;nh spin v&agrave; ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; spin.</li>\r\n<li>Reels c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng <strong>Auto Play</strong> ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng. Chu&#7897;t tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c <strong>Auto Play</strong> n&uacute;t &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y ch&#7885;n.Ch&#7885;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng spin &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#417;i t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng ho&#7863;c ch&#7885;n ''Cho &#273;&#7871;n khi t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng'' &#273;&#7875; quay cho &#273;&#7871;n khi v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o m&#7897;t t&ugrave;y ch&#7885;n kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng Auto Play. C&aacute;c <strong>Auto Play</strong> thay &#273;&#7893;i th&agrave;nh n&uacute;t <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> trong ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Play. C&aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Auto Play k&#7871;t th&uacute;c khi c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quay s&#7889; l&#7847;n x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#417;i, ho&#7863;c khi m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t n&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n ''Cho &#273;&#7871;n khi t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng'', ho&#7863;c khi b&#7841;n b&#7845;m <strong>D&#7915;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o <strong>Turbo Mode</strong> n&uacute;t c&ocirc;ng t&#7855;c ho&#7863;c t&#7855;t do &#273;&oacute; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Turbo b&#7853;t ho&#7863;c t&#7855;t m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh &#273;&#7897;ng v&agrave; &acirc;m thanh gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, v&agrave; l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n quay nhanh h&#417;n ho&#7863;c ch&#7853;m h&#417;n.</li>\r\n<li>Th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh theo paytable. D&ograve;ng gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng = c&#432;&#7907;c line X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. Scatter th&#7855;ng = t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c X nh&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo paytable. C&aacute;c paytable c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua <strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> trang.</li>\r\n<li>Tr&ecirc;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ch&#7881; c&oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng cao nh&#7845;t tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n khi th&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&ecirc;n payline kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, <strong>Win</strong> l&#297;nh v&#7921;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng t&iacute;ch l&#361;y. Win ticker c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#7915;ng l&#7841;i b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7893;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n th&#7855;ng ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c.</li>\r\n<li>th&#7855;ng payline v&agrave; t&#7893;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;n th&#7883; tr&ecirc;n d&#7843;i n&#7857;m &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a cu&#7897;n ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c c&#7917;a s&#7893; tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Trang Th&ocirc;ng tin:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Info</strong> m&#7903; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n tr&ograve; ch&#417;i kh&aacute;c nhau. Nh&#7845;p v&agrave;o n&uacute;t m&#361;i t&ecirc;n &#7903; d&#432;&#7899;i c&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cho ph&eacute;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c nhau.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh hi&#7875;n th&#7883; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng. Khi m&#7903; ra sau khi m&#7897;t spin chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, s&#7889; nh&acirc;n trao t&#7863;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&ocirc; &#273;&#7853;m v&agrave; nh&#7845;p nh&aacute;y.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Jackpot</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c c&#7911;a Progressive Jackpot, m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c Jackpot &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n cho Jackpot.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>&#273;&uacute;p</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; c&#7889; g&#7855;ng th&#7855;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i v&agrave; m&ocirc; t&#7843; c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c t&#259;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i l&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n<li>C&aacute;c <strong>Payline</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh minh h&#7885;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p payline c&oacute; th&#7875; v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c thanh to&aacute;n trong game.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Nh&#7845;p <strong>Tho&aacute;t</strong> ra kh&#7887;i c&aacute;c <strong>th&ocirc;ng tin</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v&agrave; tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho tr&ograve; ch&#417;i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>payline:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&#7919;ng line xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&ecirc;n gu&#7891;ng. Payline c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c nh&#7845;p + ho&#7863;c - d&#432;&#7899;i <strong>d&ograve;ng</strong> .</li>\r\n<li>Ch&#7881; payline &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7855;ng.</li>\r\n<li>C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c c&#432;&#7907;c line v&agrave; t&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c. D&ograve;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o m&#7897;t payline duy nh&#7845;t. T&#7893;ng c&#432;&#7907;c cho th&#7845;y bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; tr&ecirc;n v&ograve;ng ch&#417;i. Ti&#7873;n chung th&#7875; hi&#7879;n trong paytable &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7907;c line.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c quy t&#7855;c. Th&ocirc;ng tin th&ecirc;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Scatter th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>V&#7873; ti&ecirc;n chi:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c li&#7879;t k&ecirc; tr&ecirc;n <strong>paytable</strong> m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. &#272;&#7875; t&igrave;m s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng c&oacute; th&#7875;, &#273;&#7863;t c&#432;&#7907;c d&ograve;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&acirc;n v&#7899;i thanh to&aacute;n.</li>\r\n<li>N&#7871;u hai payline th&#7855;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p x&#7843;y ra tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng m&#7897;t d&ograve;ng, cao h&#417;n c&#7911;a h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi tr&#7843;. N&#7871;u c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n m&#7897;t payline &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng, th&#7855;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y.</li>\r\n<li>k&#7871;t h&#7907;p chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c cu&#7897;n l&#7841;i, v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</li>\r\n</ul>